20304.desc: Whew... At long last, after all that hard work, I get to wear this uniform as well. Even though all I did was... Huh? Lead by example? Be a role model? I don't get it...

20305.name: Norfolk
20305.desc: Norfolk-class heavy cruiser - Norfolk, Hull Number 78!

20306.name: Dorsetshire
20306.desc:
Norfolk-class heavy cruiser, Dorsetshire, Hull Number 40
<color=#fad545>Unlock build after receiving

20307.name: York
20307.desc: York-class heavy cruiser - York, Hull Number 90!

20307.name: Truth Seeker
20307.desc: The school has recently been consumed by a series of Mysteries... there must be some Mastermind lurking behind the scenes. Yes, another Tribulation awaits me! I shall part the veil and reveal all Truths!

20307.name: Summoner from the Azure Depths
20307.desc: O Unfathomable King of the slumbering depths, hear the call of my Force and step into this world through the Azur Gate! ...Huh, Commander? Why did you show up?

20307.name: Oath of Purity
20307.desc: Whoa... Is this my Uniform for the ceremony known as the Oath of Purity? Hohoho... This must be fate. Join me, Commander, and we shall make the world right once more!

20307.name: York (Retrofit)
20307.desc: This is no mere Upgrade, this is an Awakening! I will alter the course of fate itself!

20308.name: Exeter
20308.desc: York-class heavy cruiser - Exeter, Hull Number 68!

20308.name: A Glorious Toast
20308.desc: Cheers, Commander. I'm glad that the party is a success. Well, I should take care as well to not sully the honour of the royal family with my actions.

20308.name: Exeter (Retrofit)
20308.desc: Commander, what do you think? I look more mature than I did before... right?

20309.name: Sussex
20309.desc: London-class heavy cruiser, Sussex. Hull Number 96.

20309.name: Sunlit Tulips
20309.desc: What are you spacing out for? Have you not gotten tired of staring at all the swimsuits yet? Good grief... Are you able to help set up the parasol or the beach chairs at least?

20309.name: Wine and Red Roses
20309.desc: What are you staring at me for? I'm just the same as any of the others... Y-you have a few more hands to shake? Of course...

20403.name: Lady of the Shining Sun
20403.desc: What a feast for sore eyes. I feel great~! Vacations really should be at the beach! Let's show Sara your beach ball, Cygnet!

20403.name: Porcelain Grace
20403.desc: Thank you for inviting me on this wonderful trip. Now that I have donned this beautiful outfit, shall we partake of a Sakura Empire tea party– leisurely and elegantly?

20403.name: Dawnlight's Dame
20403.desc: Beauty is not always over the rainbow. Sometimes it is right in your backyard. Commander, how would you like to spend this quiet, lovely day right here with me?

20403.name: Rosey Love Poem
20403.desc: If the smooth path only allows one person to travel at a time, then I’ll gladly walk the path not taken with you hand-in-hand.

20501.name: Queen Elizabeth
20501.desc: Queen Elizabeth-class battleship - Queen Elizabeth, Hull Number 00!

20501.name: The Queen's Ball
20501.desc: Hah haah! You're a lucky servant this evening! We shall allow you to accompany us to the party! ... B-but it's not like I chose you because I like you! I just... Yes! I just sort of chose randomly! Got it?!

20501.name: One Night of the Queen
20501.desc: Now this is a stage worthy of our majesty! You are not to leave our sight, servant! Let your passions burn for me!

20501.name: Queen of the Campus
20501.desc: Hehe, behold the new outfit that I had Akashi make for me! Impressive, no? Prostrate yourself before the elegant charm of my school uniform, servant~♪

20501.name: Crown Jewel of the Royal Navy
20501.desc: Did I hear that you're supposed to give out red envelopes during the Dragon Empery's New Year? This is a fine chance to display the magnanimity of the Queen of the Royal Navy! ...Don't just run off with your gift! Spread the word of my glory, my servant!

20501.name: Yes, Your Maidness!
20501.desc: Warspite, what in the world is all this... The Maid Team has to sift through all this paperwork?! I'm tired already... I wish I never mentioned wanting to experience what it's like to be a maid... And you, stop staring and help me already, servant!

20502.name: Warspite
20502.desc: Queen Elizabeth-class battleship - Warspite, Hull Number 03!

20502.name: Christmas Warrior
20502.desc: This year, I am in charge of delivering presents to the children of the Royal Navy. Let's get going once I finish decorating this Christmas tree!

20502.name: Under Pleasure
20502.desc: We have the finest equipment. Now to turn in a performance worthy of Her Majesty's beauty... Behold, the Royal Stage!

20502.name: Warspite (Retrofit)
20502.desc: Warspite, retrofitting complete. Mm, I rather like this feeling of being rejuvenated... Now, Commander, let us make our way towards new battlegrounds!

20503.name: Luna Witch
20503.desc: This is such a weird costume… oh well, it’s Halloween after all. It cannot be so bad, this is a fun activity after all. First things first, I didn’t say that I would join from the very beginning!

20503.name: Azure & Gold Summer Night
20503.desc: Hey, are you even enjoying yourself? At least pretend to have fun when I went out of my way to invite you, or else I'm going to lose sleep over this! ...Look behind me? What are you– Oh...!

20504.name: Future Seaside Admiral
20504.desc: Although it's a gift from the Commander, it's still embarrassing to wear this....Commander, do you think you could teach me how to swim?

20504.name: Immaculate Beauty
20504.desc: Miss Akashi, shall I look at the camera next? Understood. Oh, Commander, I did not expect you to grace us with your presence here as well! Yes, the photoshoot is proceeding smoothly. By the way, is there a favorite pose you'd like to see?

20504.name: Palace of Blessings
20504.desc: I never imagined that this dreamlike situation would come to pass... Commander, have you also been looking forward to sharing this moment with me? Hehe~

20505.name: King George V
20505.desc: King George V-class battleship – King George V.

20505.name: Rose's Regalia
20505.desc: Sorry to keep you waiting, Commander... I don't get to wear a dress very often, so it took me a bit longer. Let's get going, then. Remember, you'll be the lead tonight. Haha~

20506.name: Prince of Wales
20506.desc: King George V-class battleship – Prince of Wales, Hull Number 53!

20506.name: Sun Shining Upon Windsor
20506.desc: I'm not a big fan of beach volleyball, but Hood begged me... I swear, that girl! She just can't get enough of the sun! You've got to cheer for me!

20506.name: Sakura Elegance
20506.desc: I've been wearing Royal attire my whole life, so a change in pace doesn't seem bad. Oh, Commander, good timing. Can you explain to me how to celebrate the New Year here?

20506.name: The Laureate's Victory Lap
20506.desc: Oh, Commander. Worry not. Since I've been given this job, I will see through it until the end. Besides, it's been a while since I've gotten this fired up. Haha!

20507.name: Duke of York
20507.desc: King George V-class battleship - HMS Duke of York.

20507.name: Eternal Night's Carola
20507.desc: Ahh, this luscious scent... comes from thee. What dost thee feel when gazing upon my new dress? Hehe... your lips may lie but your eyes do not...

20507.name: Prestige of the Glorious Formula
20507.desc: My beautiful Adonis, why dost thou refuseth to take refuge in the trove of everlasting love... Perhaps my outfit can finally pierce thy heart? Hehe~

20509.name: Howe
20509.desc: King George V-class battleship – Howe (HMS Howe.)

20509.name: Noble Rouge
20509.desc: Sorry to keep you waiting, but now I'm ready to– Commander? What's the matter? It'll get dark soon if you keep standing around like that.

20509.name: Pastry Princess
20509.desc: "Please, Master, save meee." ...Ugh, I can't get into the role. What sort of tone should I be aiming for, love?

20509.name: Evening Marvels
20509.desc: Thanks for your patience, love. I've looked forward to this evening's party for a long, long time. Hopefully George, York, and company won't laugh at me after how much effort I've put into this ensemble... What do you think of it, Commander?

20510.name: Mischievous Little Nurse
20510.desc: Hehe~ As this medical facility training is crucially important, a charismatic leader such as myself would be best suited to instruct everyone on– Wait a moment, what's with this outfit?! You there, explain the meaning of this at once!

20510.name: Queen Valiant I
20510.desc: Why the astonished look on your face? You heard me correctly! On this day, I am not merely Valiant, I am the regal and royal Queen Valiant!

20511.name: The Maid-Knight Charges Forth!
20511.desc: Hrmm... *sigh*... Looks like I bungled this one too... I sure hope the Commander doesn't see me like th– Hwuh?! C-Commander? P-please give me a moment! I'll straighten this out right away... Waaah!!

20513.name: Half-Hearted Masquerade
20513.desc: "Please let me know if you need anything, Master"... I'm starting to think you're making me wear this as a sick joke. The reason being, I am obviously NOT fit to be a Royal Maid... Even if I do adore their uniforms...

20514.name: Bashful Oak
20514.desc: Commander? Oh, what a coincidence... Were you slacking– err, I mean, taking a break, too? I can make some room for you if you'd like?

20601.name: Hermes
20601.desc: Hermes-class aircraft carrier – Hermes, Hull Number 95!

20601.name: Hermes (Retrofit)
20601.desc: Our glory coalesces into the bonds that forge a bright new future! Let's rev it up! Hermes, retrofit complete!

20602.name: A Hundred Sleepless Eyes
20602.desc: Yaaawn... Umm, did I doze off again? Oh no... Organising school events gets so hectic I always end up working right up until curfew... Just give me one more minute, please...

20603.name: Unicorn
20603.desc: Aircraft carrier – Unicorn, Hull Number I72!

20603.name: Little Star Songstress
20603.desc: Unicorn... is now a songstress... *giggles* Unicorn's song has reached Onii-chan's heart.

20603.name: The Gift of Spring
20603.desc: This... present... is for you... I hope you like it... What? Me wearing this outfit is the best gift I can give you? Co... Commander!...

20603.name: Long-Awaited Date
20603.desc: Ah, big brother, you're here... Ehehe, I only just got here as well. Um... shall we go then? I kind of... want to go to the amusement park...

20603.name: Prayer of Plum and Snow
20603.desc: So this is a "kimono" from the Sakura Empire... Changing into it is difficult but... if you like it, then Unicorn is happy!

20603.name: Angelic Night
20603.desc: So I'm... an "idol" now... I'm not sure how well I'll do... But I'll give it my all...!

20603.name: Icy-Sweet Storytime
20603.desc: Oh, big brother... Unicorn is reading right now. Mm, yeah, while eating ice cream... Big brother, want to have a bite?

20603.name: A Dream of Pure Vows
20603.desc: This is... an important outfit for an important ceremony... yes! Unicorn and Yuni are both ready for this! Big brother... how do I look?

20603.name: Unicorn (Retrofit)
20603.desc: Unicorn has finished her retrofit... Now she can do more for you and her friends!

20604.name: Beachside Undine
20604.desc: Even though I see the ocean every day, changing into this swimsuit gives me a totally new outlook on it. How about you, Commander? Don't you feel at ease?

20604.name: Sprightly Spring Wind
20604.desc: I never imagined you would give me such a splendid dress, Commander... I think it's called a "qipao..." is it? I'll try it, revealing though it is. Wh- what do you think...? Do I look... nice?

20605.name: The Way of the Dragon Empery
20605.desc: Does this dress from the Dragon Empery not suit me well? Though I was born in the Eagle Union and raised by the Royal Navy, my time in the Dragon Empery also left a deep impression upon me. Why don't we have a chat about their profound culture and tea? Hehe~

20605.name: Gamer Style
20605.desc: Heck yeah! Another achievement down! ...Huh? Good day, Commander. Is there something wrong with my appearance? Hehe, I'm from the Eagle Union after all, of course I'd know a thing or two about entertainment~♪

20606.name: Perseus
20606.desc: Colossus-class light aircraft carrier – Perseus (HMS Perseus.)

20606.name: Unfamiliar Duties
20606.desc: I'm Perseus, I will be your nurse today. Use this button to call for me if you need anything... Yes? Did you need something?

20607.name: Silvermoon Faerie Princess
20607.desc: Ah, umm... If you keep staring at me like that... Oh, um, Commander, this is supposed to be a Royalty of the Night costume, right? In that case... Would you mind kneeling for me first?

20608.name: New Year's White Plumage
20608.desc: Steaming hot manjuu buns, ready to be served! Let us have a big feast then gather rosebuds, Commander. Oh, a "holiday gathering" doesn't involve literal gathering?

20701.name: Eagle
20701.desc: Eagle-class light aircraft carrier – Eagle (HMS Eagle.)

20701.name: Eagle's Clinic
20701.desc: This may be an exercise, but even so I will give it my all. Right now, I am not just a Royal Navy warrior, but a medical resident as well. If you ever feel ill, come see me, Commander.

20702.name: Ark Royal
20702.desc: Aircraft carrier – Ark Royal, Hull Number 91!

20702.name: Coast Watcher
20702.desc: Nothing says summer like the sun, the beach, and destroyers... Ahem! Th-that's right! Even though we're relaxing, we still have to keep an eye out for enemy destroyers! Commander, I may be in a swimsuit, but I'm ready to sortie at any time!

20702.name: Guardian of the Ball
20702.desc: One tends to let her guard down at a party like this, but worry not! Put the ball in my hands and let Ark Royal keep you safe!

20702.name: New Year's Protectress
20702.desc: Commander, Happy New Year. Oh no, I'm not going hunting. I'm patrolling the port during the New Year's celebrations. Naturally, I volunteered for the job.

20702.name: Café Lookout
20702.desc: This is the place, Commander. What are you going to order? Me, I think I'll have the same as you... Yeah, so what? I just felt like grabbing a coffee with you for once.

20702.name: Pure-White Protector
20702.desc: I never thought a day would come when even I don such attire... Ahem. Your Excellency, I shall protect your happiness, as well as that of my destroyer sisters!

20702.name: Ark Royal (Retrofit)
20702.desc: Ark Royal retrofitting complete! Now I can protect you, my friends, and of course, the little destroyers, to the very end!

20703.name: Illustrious
20703.desc: Illustrious-class aircraft carrier – Illustrious, Hull Number 87!

20703.name: Never-Ending Tea Party
20703.desc: Sun kissed skin, scrumptious snacks and delicious black tea. It’s as if both my mind and body have been rejuvenated— Commander, care to join me for some leisurely chit-chat?

20703.name: Illustrious Ball
20703.desc: An invitation to the ball? Hehe, I would be honored to go... as long as you don't decline, Commander~

20703.name: Resplendent Hibiscus
20703.desc: This is my first time wearing such exotic fashion, hehe~. Commander, if you like how I look, how about showing me off a little~?

20703.name: Maiden Lily's Radiance
20703.desc: It is my honour to get to wear another faction's garments. However... this traditional Dragon Empery dress feels rather tight around the chest area...

20703.name: Morning Star of Love and Hope
20703.desc: The end of sorrow, the beginning of happiness, and the desire for eternity.

20704.name: The Goddess' Day Off
20704.desc: Hum~ dee dum♪~ I'm all dressed up, and my hair is perfect! Commander, I'm ready to go! Don't keep me waiting on a holiday!

20704.name: Guidance of the Spring Goddess
20704.desc: Are you preparing to hold an event for the port? Hehe, sounds like you could use my help. Don't worry, with someone as beautiful as me around, anything you do will surely be blessed with success!

20705.name: The Lady of the Beach
20705.desc: Good day, Commander. I am Formidable, third ship of the Illustrious class. Pleased to make your acquaintance.

20705.name: Timeless Classics
20705.desc: Yes, this will do wonderfully! Thank you, ladies. Phew... Getting dressed is so dreadfully time-consuming... Ahem! How silly of me. I must not whine in the presence of others.

20706.name: Glorious
20706.desc: Courageous-class aircraft carrier – Glorious, Hull Number 77.

20706.name: Glorious School Life
20706.desc: Being able to occasionally have a peaceful school life... is something I could get used to. Commander, look at the markings on this butterfly - aren't they lovely?

20706.name: Pungent Plum
20706.desc: I heard that the Sakura Empire's traditional attire was really hard to put on... but the Dragon's Empery's outfits are even more... Huh?! Commander, p-please look away!

20707.name: Shepherd of the "Lost"
20707.desc: Oh my... It seems I've shown you a rather unseemly side of me. Would you help me clean up here, Commander? You know... before any of the other girls find out. Heehee~♥

20709.name: Little Illustrious
20709.desc: Illustrious-class aircraft carrier – Illustrious, Hull Number 87.

20711.name: Illustrious μ
20711.desc: I am the newest addition to the Muse System, Illustrious. Through my songs, I shall spread the light of love and peace— Don't you think that's a wonderful thing?

20712.name: Ms. Motivationless Maid
20712.desc: *Sigh*... I thought changing into maid attire would break up the monotony, but just getting into these clothes has tired me out... Oh, Commander? You came at a good time. Shall we slack off together?

21301.name: Erebus
21301.desc: Erebus-class monitor – Erebus, Hull Number I02!

21301.name: Illusory Happiness
21301.desc: Those who embrace the shadows will find only an illusory happiness... But for me, that much is sufficient.

21301.name: Wardrobe Witchery
21301.desc: "I am the witch of Hallow's Eve, here to guide your soul into the ever darkness"... that's what the concept of the Halloween witch is about, right?

21302.name: Terror
21302.desc: Erebus-class monitor – Terror, Hull Number I03!

21302.name: Halloween Terror
21302.desc: I have to dress up as a ghost for Halloween, but I'm not very good at making complicated costumes... Is something like this okay?

21304.name: Abercrombie
21304.desc: Roberts-class monitor - Abercrombie. Hull Number F109.

21304.name: Pumpkin Blast!
21304.desc: Kabooom! You thought it was a pumpkin, but it was me, Abercrombie, with my Mark I! Commander, did I scare you senseless? Muahaha!

21304.name: Mischief on the Rocks
21304.desc: Now for a ghost pepper while nobody's looking... Tee hee! Perfect! I wonder who'll be the lucky one to sip– C-Commander?! You didn't see anything suspicious... Right? Tee hee~

29901.name: Princess of the Reindeers
29901.desc: Hehe~ I usually let the other girls have all the glory, but even I must sometimes give you something to remember me by. Merry Christmas, Commander~

29901.name: Nereid's Invitation
29901.desc: Welcome to our celebration, Commander. At this breathtaking venue, I, Neptune, shall be the one to show you around, rather than the Royal Maids. Heehee~♪

29902.name: White Warrick
29902.desc: Hmph. One's outfit is merely superficial. True nobility must come from within. Don't you agree, Commander?

29902.name: Black Gerard
29902.desc: So, an Eastern outfit this time... Hmph. My nobility is evident regardless of what I wear. However, since you prepared this outfit especially for me, it would be unbecoming of me to not express my gratitude. Thank you.

29903.name: Summery Date!
29903.desc: Cheer up, Owner! Jeez, why are you so bummed out when we're at the beach... Because it's just a normal playdate instead of a romantic date? What's the difference anyway? C'mon, let's go head down to where the others are~!

29903.name: Cait Sith Crooner
29903.desc: I'll sing a song for you, Owner~ Ahem... Wait, I'm not sure I know any Dragon Empery songs, actually...

29903.name: The Cat and the White Steed
29903.desc: "Owner~ I've come to take you to the ball~" ...That's exactly what you were going to do? Eh, doesn't matter who does it~ All that matters is we'll be there together~♪

29904.name: The Golden Hind's Respite
29904.desc: Phew... Swimming like this doesn't feel all that refreshing... Hey, how about you stop staring and come join me?

29905.name: Heart-Throbbing Refreshment
29905.desc: Rejoice, Commander. I have no doubt that this refreshing sensation will bring you the utmost satisfaction. Come, let us enjoy this experience together.

30101.name: Fubuki
30101.desc: Special type I Fubuki Destroyer Class— Fubuki

30101.name: 5 Minutes Till I'm Late
30101.desc: Oh no! I-I'm gonna be late for school! Y-you need to speed up too, doggy! *Pant*... *pant*... Why'd none of my sisters wake me up before they left?!

30101.name: Mascot Bucky
30101.desc: "C-come on in! We've got special offers for you!" ... W-wait, is this really what a "sexy mascot" would wear? It feels pretty different from what I was expecting... And boy, is it stuffy in this thing...

30101.name: Music Pixy
30101.desc: Check it out, Commander! What do you think? ... No, not my dress! I'm talking about the tuba! Want me to play a tune for you~?

30101.name: Fubuki Halation!
30101.desc: The whole world's going to feel the tremors from my debut! I'm Fubuki, the Special-type idol!

30101.name: Stormy Waitress-in-Training!
30101.desc: Welcome, welcome! Oh, Commander! I've actually started working here part-time, but I'm still learning— Wooah?! Phew... Th-that was a close one...

30102.name: Shirayuki
30102.desc: Special Type I-class destroyer number two – Shirayuki.

30102.name: Bunny Breeder
30102.desc: Whoa now! There's enough food for everyone, so don't fight over it! ...Commander? Don't just stand there, give me a hand, please!

30104.name: Miyuki
30104.desc: Special Type I Fubuki-class destroyer number four – Miyuki.

30104.name: Shopping Rendezvous
30104.desc: Commander, I think the goods over here are a bit cheaper... Umm, I'm doing fine on my budget still, so we can pick out some more things to buy. A-also, I'll get to spend more time shopping with you... Ah, d-disregard that please... *blushes*

30105.name: Ayanami
30105.desc: First ship of special Type II Ayanami class destroyers, Ayanami.

30105.name: Witch in Ambush
30105.desc: I heard that... I need to wear a costume like this to participate in Halloween festivities. Commander... do I look cute?

30105.name: Rock 'n' Demon
30105.desc: Commander, want to listen to music together? Do you like... this non-combat-oriented Ayanami?

30105.name: Lunar Demon
30105.desc: Compared to the way we celebrate New Year in the Sakura Empire, the festivities of the Dragon Empery have a completely different atmosphere... But, I don't really mind the liveliness... Commander, do you like festivals?

30105.name: Grade A Sailor Uniform
30105.desc: "Welcome, Commander..." I should greet customers like this... yes?

30105.name: Covert Ops Cloak
30105.desc: Ayanami here. Successfully infiltrated Commander's office. Oh... Commander saw me. Operation failed...

30105.name: Low-Key Idol @Confused
30105.desc: I guess I'm making my idol debut? Um, Javelin and the others are making their debuts, so, I also had to... Commander, what are idols supposed to do normally?

30105.name: Demon's Finest Dress
30105.desc: This dress is... Ayanami’s. I'm not used to this dress yet... Commander, do you think it fits me?

30105.name: Ayanami (Retrofit)
30105.desc: Ayanami, retrofit complete. I feel stronger, yes... Having that said, Commander, can you pat my head? I want to be spoiled a bit...

30105.name: Pulse of the New Year
30105.desc: Commander, Happy New Year's. In this coming year, please continue to look after me...

30105.name: Nightfall Raiment
30105.desc: Commander, thank you for coming to the party. Ayanami... has been waiting for you. ...I look a bit scary? I'm not sure I get it... I guess.

30105.name: Off-Duty Battle Station Gear
30105.desc: No, Ryuujou! Samurai builds should stay back during the boss! ...Oh, welcome, Commander. I'm busy with this game right now, so just make yourself at home or something.

30105.name: Cola Fills You With Determination
30105.desc: Welcome. Ayanami will be taking your order, yes. Will this be dine-in, or to-go? I would personally recommend the cola.

30105.name: Dynamic Kick!
30105.desc: Ultimate Ability: Dynamic Kick! ...Oh, I used my skill on the wrong target. Sorry, can we try that again?

30109.name: Akatsuki
30109.desc: Type III Akatsuki-class destroyer number one - Akatsuki.

30109.name: Akatsuki Goes North
30109.desc: Is this the place called the Northern Parliament?! It is colder than I thought... Th-thank goodness I brought gear for extreme environments! Hibiki, please wait a bit longer! Your sister is coming to see you!

30109.name: Motoninja Akatsuki
30109.desc: What do you think, Commander? I have a brand new outfit and a brand new companion! I am no longer a plain old ninja... I am now a motoninja!

30109.name: Santa's Lost Helper!
30109.desc: Look out! Move, Commander! ...Phew. To explain, I am helping Santa give out Christmas presents! Now excuse me, I cannot tarry here or I'll be late... Wait, have I come to the wrong place? WHAT?!

30109.name: Cirque de Ninjutsu!
30109.desc: Welcome, Commander, to DesDiv 6's tent of entertainment! For our first act, I shall perform for you my most stunning ninjutsu! ..."Circus"? I've never heard of this word before!

30110.name: Hibiki
30110.desc: Type III Akatsuki-class destroyer number two – Hibiki.

30110.name: New Year's Little Imp
30110.desc: New Year's finally comes to port! I, Hibiki of the 6th DesDiv, will be marking my new arrival in my New Year's attire! Commander, don't you dare change the channel - you've gotta watch my every move~!

30111.name: Ikazuchi
30111.desc: Type III Akatsuki-class destroyer number three - Ikazuchi.

30111.name: Sakura Tea
30111.desc: Ikazuchi, Ikazuchi has been transformed into tea! What should we do! Inazuma and Ikazuchi will get slurped up by the Commander!

30111.name: Thunderous Festival
30111.desc: Inazuma and I have been to a lot of festivals together, but this would be the first time that I've gone with you, Commander. Isn't this totally like a date?

30111.name: Dawn's Thunder
30111.desc: I'm the fairy of thunder that shatters the night to herald the dawn! I see, I see! That is a good backstory! Commander, want to head to the party together?

30112.name: Inazuma
30112.desc: Type III Akatsuki-class destroyer number four - Inazuma.

30112.name: Vanilla Pudding
30112.desc: It doesn’t matter if Inazuma becomes Mr. Commander's dessert… but if Inazuma cannot be found, Mr. Commander will feel so devastated, perhaps he won’t be able to command the fleet… so… please! Please convey Inazuma's heartfelt wish to Mr. Commander——

30112.name: Flash of Fireworks
30112.desc: I usually go to festivals with Ikazuchi, but this would be my first time going with you. Hmm? Where should we visit first?

30112.name: Dusk's Lightning
30112.desc: I'm the fairy of lightning that illuminates the stars in the night sky... So that's what we're going with, huh. Commander, will you accompany me to the party?

30113.name: Is The Order A Torpedo?
30113.desc: H-here they come... Your order, and your cutesy dutesy maid... Whoaahh! I'm sorry! Look out!

30114.name: Shogun of Snowballs
30114.desc: Come out of your office, Commander! You'll become lazy if you huddle up next to the heater all day! Let's go out and play in the snow!

30114.name: Carnivore Carnival!
30114.desc: Commander, look at me, look at me! What do you think of my new outfit? If you like it, wanna give it a feel?

30114.name: Woofy Floofy Christmas Night
30114.desc: Christmas! The day Santa Claus drops by and leaves presents, right? Hell yeah, I'm pumped! Aren't you pumped too, Commander?

30114.name: The Bride of Solomon
30114.desc: Commander, look! Look at this new dress. Red and white, I really really like it! But what's the occasion?

30114.name: Yuudachi (Retrofit)
30114.desc: Woof...? Am I imagining it, or did you get shorter, Commander? Unless... it's me who's gotten bigger? Seriously?! Nobody told me retrofitting makes you taller!

30115.name: Attack, I-490!
30115.desc: Stupid Commander, I'm not a damn submarine! Do you wanna get hit in the face with an oxygen torpedo?

30115.name: The Ballroom's Lucky Star
30115.desc: Oh my. Commander, you must be pretty lucky to bump into me here, hehe~ Since you're here, you can have the privilege of being my escort tonight. Now, be grateful~♪

30115.name: Lucky Chocolate
30115.desc: All right, that should be good... Hey, stupid Commander standing around aimlessly. Yeah, you. Stick your hand out. You're gonna be the first person to get MY chocolate, so I'd better see some tears of gratitude.

30115.name: Shigure (Retrofit)
30115.desc: Heheh~ Retrofitting the mighty Shigure proves that you are quite perceptive! Aren't you glad that you get to rely on me more, you lucky idiot of a commander~♪

30116.name: Sovereign of the Swing
30116.desc: Wa ha ha! My "universal-as-long-as-there-is-a-ceiling" swing set is finally complete! Commander, are you jealous? Want to give it a try? Too~ bad~! This seat is reserved only for the noble and elegant Yukikaze!

30116.name: Winter's Snowy Wind
30116.desc: Wa ha ha~! Did your heart skip a beat from seeing the charming Yukikaze? Hmph... Well, looks like the Dragon Empery girls are setting off firecrackers... let's go join them! Here, make sure to hold on to my hand!

30116.name: The Warmth of Spring
30116.desc: This outfit is sooo cute~ ehehe... Ack!! *cough* *cough*! Ahem! From now on, you are the faithful companion of Yukikaze the Great! As such, you will not be permitted to leave my side, understood?

30117.name: Pumpkins and Festivities!
30117.desc: Commander, trick or treat! I expect you to give some candy to my sisters as well! These will-o'-wisps? Hahaha~ I tried imitating that gloomy sister of mine!

30117.name: Kagerou (Retrofit)
30117.desc: The newly-retrofitted Kagerou has arrived~ I won't let that sister of mine pass me up anymore! Commander, lead us forward towards distant shores!

30118.name: Mooncake Merchant
30118.desc: I see a chance... to capitalize on the Dragon Empery's famous mooncakes... Commander, would you like to have a taste of the Moon Palace's delicacies? If you buy them in bulk, I'll give you a special discount.

30118.name: Shiranui (Retrofit)
30118.desc: If you have this much money remaining... then you may visit me and spend it with confidence... A discount, you say...? Of course... Someday, I shall give you one...

30121.name: Snow Day Hatsuharu
30121.desc: Everyone's playing together...? I-I think I'll pass... Y-you want me to join them? Ugh, well, if you say so, then I-I-I'll try to socialize with them...!

30121.name: Hatsuharu in the Limelight
30121.desc: C-Commander, I will be your partner for the party tonight. Let's see, umm... I believe this is proper Royal Navy etiquette... D-did I do it correctly?

30121.name: Hatsuharu (Retrofit)
30121.desc: Hatsuharu, retrofit complete... H-hopefully I'm a little bit stronger now...

30123.name: Holiday Special Wakaba!
30123.desc: Yaho~ Good morning, Commander! For a limited time only, Wakaba Claus will be delivering Christmas presents! Huh? My bag? Aaahhh! C-Commander, help me pick everything up!

30123.name: A Healthy Dose of Sunshine!
30123.desc: Hmmgh! Oh yeah... Ah, there you are, Commander! Care to join me? Come bask in the afternoon sunshine, it feels great!

30124.name: Perennial Joy
30124.desc: Cheers, Commander~ C'mere, you've got to enjoy the party too! If you're thinking of doing something tactless like running off to go back to work, people are going to get upset with you~

30124.name: Hatsushimo (Retrofit)
30124.desc: Hatsushimo's retrofitting is complete. You don't think I look all that different? Oh, Commander, you're still as simple as ever~ I've changed in tons of ways beyond what's just on the surface. Heheheh~

30125.name: Unending Friendship
30125.desc: Hope everyone enjoys the oodles of balloons I made for this party! Yeah, I'm sure the little girls will love 'em!

30125.name: Ariake (Retrofit)
30125.desc: Ah... So this is what it feels like to be retrofitted. I'll work harder for your sake, and for everyone in the 27th Destroyer Division~

30126.name: Yuugure
30126.desc: Sixth ship of Hatsuharu class Destroyer— Yuugure

30126.name: Maid-In-Training!
30126.desc: "I, Yuugure the maid, shall dedicate myself to Ariake, my sister, and you, Commander!"... Eek?! M-my skirt...!

30126.name: Twilight Blossom
30126.desc: The Dragon Empery's New Year celebrations and new outfits are sure to lift everyone's spirits~ My sister will probably love this new dress as well. Commander, what do you think?

30126.name: Evening Flower
30126.desc: I finished changing, Commander. This dress is very pretty, but... isn't it missing something up top?

30126.name: Summer Festival Shopping
30126.desc: Woah... These stalls have all sorts of amazing things~ Commander, will you help me pick a gift out for Ariake? Hm, let's see... How about this Daruma doll?

30126.name: Fun in the Sun
30126.desc: I was really looking forward to playing with you at the beach, Commander, so I changed into this swimsuit. Umm... Ariake told me that I had to choose something that was easy to move around in, and cute enough to make you lose your mind... Was she pulling my leg?

30126.name: Yuugure (Retrofit)
30126.desc: Ariake-class destroyer, Yuugure, has completed retrofitting. Ehehe, from now on... Ariake and I will be in your care once more, Commander.

30129.name: World's Speediest Bunny Waitress
30129.desc: Hippity hoppity! Grab a glass and have a sippity! Whew, I must say, this outfit was tricky to get into. Still, you made an exquisite pick, Commander!

30129.name: The White Rabbit of Wonderland
30129.desc: Whoa-whoa-whoa! Why'd I end up here again?! Even though I've been running for a whole hour! ...Commander?! Waaaah, I'm so glad to see you! Please, help me get out of heeeeeeere!

30129.name: The Island Wind Rests
30129.desc: You can't keep sprinting across the sea forever. Sometimes, you need to rest and recover your strength. Speaking of, you may use my parasol if you like, Commander!

30130.name: Kamikaze (Retrofit)
30130.desc: Ohohoho, you must have a sharp eye if you've decided to retrofit me~ Now that I've been chosen, I cannot afford to embarrass you. Now, take a good and thorough look at this veteran's aspirations~

30131.name: Matsukaze (Retrofit)
30131.desc: There we go... My fan is too big, and I'm not used to carrying it around yet... Ah, right, come here for a sec, Commander~ I'll fan you with some cool air~ Come on now, no need to be shy~

30132.name: Mr. Reindeer, Depart!
30132.desc: Commander, Merry Christmas~! I am on my best behavior today as well! Uuu... when is Santa Claus going to come? I'm sleepy...

30132.name: Candy Festival!
30132.desc: Comainder, I put on my yukata just like you said! Ehehe, you should take me to the festival so I can get lots and lots of candy!

30132.name: Spring Festival Sweets
30132.desc: I heard that if I go around telling people "Happy New Year," I can get lots of goodies! Ehehe, I hope they'll give me a bunch of candy!

30132.name: Mutsuki (Retrofit)
30132.desc: Comainder, I'm done retrofitting! Have some candy! Hm? You're always nice to me, so I'm giving you some candy!

30133.name: New Year's Wish
30133.desc: Co... commander, Kisaragi's new outfit... How does it look? It's a new year... Kisaragi wants to keep improving...

30133.name: Kisaragi (Retrofit)
30133.desc: Kisaragi... retrofitting complete... I want to be able to help everyone out more...

30135.name: Uzuki
30135.desc: The fourth ship of Mutsuki class destroyer — Uzuki

30135.name: Sleepy Uzuki
30135.desc: Ah... Big sis Kisaragi, big sis Mutsuki, let's sleep together... Commander? You want to come too?

30138.name: Sleepy Fairy
30138.desc: Huh...? Where am I...? What time is it...?

30139.name: Dangerous Kitty Maid?
30139.desc: Nagatsuki the kitty maid is at your service~ Do your best to not fall madly in love with my cute looks~! Hehe~

30141.name: Sweet Zombie
30141.desc: Mikazuki is supposed to be... a jiangshi? Um... hip... hop... Commander, trick or treaaaaat~

30147.name: Soft and Fluffy Therapy
30147.desc: What's the matter, Commander? Oh, this outfit? ...Um, I heard that this outfit would bring you therapeutic benefits and hoped to try it on... Wh-what do you think? Does it feel therapeutic to you?

30147.name: Baby Steps
30147.desc: Commander, it is my pleasure to accompany you today. Umm... What do you think? I decided to go for a different outfit this time... D-do you think it's cute?

30148.name: Now for a Magic Trick!
30148.desc: Voilà! Don't go anywhere, Commander! My magic show will start in just a sec! To start with, let's hear a roar! Roooaar!

30149.name: Monochromatic Interlude
30149.desc: Mhm. Lightweight clothing makes it easier to fight. Thanks, Commander... "It looks cute on me"? W-well, thanks...

30149.name: Unsullied White Fox
30149.desc: This must be the dream you've awaited so eagerly... Of course, I vowed to be with you until the end of our days. I shall take my rightful place beside you and your ideals. We are... together.

30154.name: Festive Riding Hood?
30154.desc: S-sorry to keep you waiting... Yuugure and I picked out this outfit together. She said it "looked very Christmassy," but it doesn't look weird, right? ... Ugh...

30157.name: A Dance for the Coming Spring
30157.desc: Happy New Year, Commander! I am currently on my way to give a Kagura dance at the shrine. If you have time... would you like to come see it?

30158.name: Sports Festival Preparations
30158.desc: It's my turn? Hold on... Umm, could you please not stare at me like that? It's... making me feel uncomfortable.

30158.name: Firecrackers and Steamed Buns
30158.desc: Mmh... Happy New Year. I'm working on hooking my friends up with these firecrackers... The bun I'm eating? I received it as a thank-you for my efforts.

30159.name: Urakaze
30159.desc: The 11th Destroyer of Kagerou class — Urakaze

30159.name: Seasonal Shogun
30159.desc: Before you raise a fuss about it, let me just tell you this - the concept of "Christmas" already existed during the Sengoku period, so there's nothing weird about putting on a Christmas outfit!

30159.name: Sengoku☆Shredder!
30159.desc: Ugh... Even though we finally got all our gear, we still need more band members... Commander! Stop complaining and come hither! From now on, you're a member of the Sengoku Shredders!

30160.name: New Year's Campaign
30160.desc: General, General, look! It's my New Year's outfit! Urakaze made it for me! Let's play a bunch of Sengoku wargames this year as well!

30160.name: Sengoku☆Smasher!
30160.desc: General! I, Isokaze, have done my utmost to prepare the equipment! Now, with Lord Urakaze's presence, our Sengoku☆War-Band is complete! Of course, you are more than welcome to join our ranks, General!

30161.name: Hamakaze
30161.desc: Tenth ship of Kagerou class destroyers, Hamakaze.

30161.name: The Honors Student
30161.desc: Learning is exciting. The joy of acquiring new knowledge, the sense of achievement from solving difficult problems... you'll understand once you try it. So, shall we study together, Commander?

30161.name: The Secret Ingredient is Love?!
30161.desc: I'm experimenting with different flavors since we're running a pop-up café... Alright! I think I'll go with this one! Strap in, Commander, because you're about to do a lot of taste-testing!

30161.name: Hamakaze (Retrofit)
30161.desc: Commander, have you been having more fun since I arrived? ... I see, that's great! Ehehe... Hamakaze, getting hyped!

30162.name: Lost Girl and Labyrinth Butterfly
30162.desc: Little butterfly, little butterfly... Ya! It flew away... Hamakaze~ Hamakaze~ Where are you? Urakaze? Isokaze? We said we were going to play at the seaside. Where is everyone?

30162.name: Sparkly-Clean
30162.desc: Commander, I'm mopping the floor right now. Please watch your step, as it's quite slippery over there... Eek! Owch... I suppose I should've watched my own step... Ahaha...

30162.name: Tanikaze (Retrofit)
30162.desc: I'm Tanikaze, blowing and blustering from the mountaintop! Whoa! Butterflies? Butterflies?! Look, butterflies! For me? Thanks, Commander!

30163.name: The Transfer Student Underneath the Dancing Petals
30163.desc: My name is Asashio, and I just transferred here today. Pleased to meet you... Even though I might not be able to get caught up with the course work, Mr. Kitty and I will do our best.

30163.name: Snow-Dusted Lynx Tips
30163.desc: Happy New Year, Commander. I am here to spend the New Year with you. Would you be so kind as to first help me down from here?

30163.name: Robes of Dancing Clouds
30163.desc: Commander, thank you for coming to see me. I'm currently rehearsing my program for the Spring Festival performance. I do hope it is to your liking.

30164.name: The Reindeer's Present
30164.desc: Merry Christmas~ Commander, we gotta go hand out presents to them destroyers~ You be Santa, I'll be yer reindeer~

30164.name: Woozy Party
30164.desc: Happy anniversary~ Today's a day to enjoy to yer heart's content, ya know? I'm just havin' fun in my own way, checkin' out cute girls from afar~ I appreciate yer concern though, Commander~

30164.name: Bringer of Fortunes
30164.desc: Should I hang this "fortune" poster here...? Oh, Commander, did ya also want a Spring Festival present from Ooshio here? Just kiddin'~ Hehe, anyway, happy Lunar New Year~

30164.name: Let's 'ave Lunch
30164.desc: Finally we're through with them mornin' classes~ Commander, would ya fancy havin' lunch with me? Heheh, yer wonderin' what I done made? You'll see for yerself soon 'nuff~

30165.name: Michishio
30165.desc: Third ship of Asashio class destroyers, Michishio.

30165.name: Fluttering Fanfare
30165.desc: Hello, Commander. Oh, you think I look good in this fluttery dress~? Thank you very much!

30166.name: The Gentlest Firework
30166.desc: Looks like you found me, Commander. Hehe, want to light some fireworks with me? Spending time together should be more fun than being alone, right?

30172.name: Uranami
30172.desc: Special Type I-class destroyer number 10 – Uranami.

30172.name: Snow Vanguard
30172.desc: It's snowing...! I've finished rallying the forces... so let us advance!

30180.name: Time for School!
30180.desc: All right, everything looks good! I'm super excited and my batteries are fully charged! I'm heading out~!

30181.name: New Year's Comfort
30181.desc: Warm and comforting clothes... Warm and comforting red bean soup... Ahh, I love New Year's.

30181.name: At School with Foo
30181.desc: Kasumi and Foo are excited about the new semester. Are you too, Commander?

30181.name: Kasumi (Retrofit)
30181.desc: Kasumi thinks that her outfit has gotten a bit breezier. Foo said the same thing.

30182.name: Morning Moon, Beachside Flower
30182.desc: I've heard some say that summer is the season of cherry blossoms, lotus petals, and sunflowers, but... If you ask me, being able to leisurely enjoy the breeze with you feels pretty good too. Hehe~

30182.name: Blossoming Spring, Resplendent Moon
30182.desc: What kinds of flowers should I decorate the office with for the Lunar New Year...? Ugh, I just can't decide! Um, Commander, will you be inspecting the interior? I'll show you around! Phew...

30183.name: Long Waves of Happiness
30183.desc: Akashi pushed me into getting this outfit, saying that it would surely make you happy, but... What do you think...?

30183.name: Long-Awaited Warmth
30183.desc: There's still some time before the banquet begins, and I'm afraid I'm feeling a little sleepy... W-would you mind if I took a nap? Thank you...

30183.name: Nestling Up for the Long Nights
30183.desc: I wanted to help you relieve some stress, so I thought I would read some folk tales to you... When I mentioned that, Akashi suggested these clothes to me... Wh-what do you think?

30183.name: Waves of Eternal Love
30183.desc: Now that the big day is here, I'm awfully nervous... I-I'll be in your care now and forever, okay?

30184.name: Suzutsuki, Beachside Attendant!
30184.desc: Commander, over here! We're about to start without you! Ahaha, what would you like to do, Commander? Beach volleyball? Sandcastle building? We can also go relax in the water if you'd like!

30184.name: Suzutsuki, Hanetsuki Adept!
30184.desc: I, Akizuki-class destroyer, Suzutsuki, shall not allow you to pass through these arches! Hwuh?! I missed the return again...!

30185.name: Summer Dedication
30185.desc: Commander, have you also come to play on the beach? You're telling me to be careful? Hmph, what misfortune could possibly befall me from a game of watermelon splitting... Gwaah?!

30185.name: Jet Ink, Silver Quills
30185.desc: Happy New Year to you, Commander. To celebrate the season, I had these garments tailor-made for me, using traditional Dragon Empery clothes as a basis. I don't look... childish, do I?

30186.name: After-School Melody
30186.desc: Toot~♪ Oh, Commander, did you hear me practicing my recorder? Umm, I'd appreciate it if you didn't tell the others.

30186.name: Placid Waves, Passionate Heart
30186.desc: *lick*... Oh, Commander, y-you're here for the fireworks? ...Want to watch them with me, then? I've got drinks. My ice cream? Umm... You can't have it.

30188.name: Slapdash Blue Sparrow
30188.desc: Oh nooo! Look out, Commander! ...Oh, phew... I'm glad I didn't mess up your clothes because of my carelessness! Please forgive me for my blunder! I'll clean the floor up right away!

30201.name: Yuubari (Retrofit)
30201.desc: I've finally finished developing my new equipment! Since we still have time, let's go and try it out in live combat right now, Master!

30204.name: Nagara
30204.desc: First ship of the Nagara-class light cruisers, Nagara.

30204.name: Spring Breeze Leisure
30204.desc: Good evening, Commander. This room...? Ah, it's a special Dragon Empery-themed set I bought from Akashi's. It looks pretty snazzy and was on sale, so I picked it up. Ehehe~

30205.name: Isuzu
30205.desc: Second ship of the Nagara-class light cruisers, Isuzu.

30205.name: Night of Fairy Tale
30205.desc: There will be lots and lots of ghosts and spirits during Halloween... I, I’m not afraid!... say, can, can you hold my hand?

30205.name: Cozy Christmas Eve
30205.desc: Commander? I only came here to help wrap up all the presents for tomorrow, n-not because the fireplace is too cozy and I don't want to get up...

30205.name: Accidental Overheat?
30205.desc: Wooah! ...I fell down again... But at least it's cooler now... Huh? A photoshoot? Noo, don't take a picture of me~

30205.name: Charge, My Trusty Steeds!
30205.desc: W-w-woah! W-wait up! You guys are going too fast! I'm gonna fall! I'm gonna faaaaall! You're supposed to carry me in a way that doesn't give me a heart attack!! Commander, something crazy seems to have happened with my cavalry~!!

30205.name: Isuzu (Retrofit)
30205.desc: Retrofit complete! ...Umm, Commander? ...Wh-what's the matter? Do I really look that different...?!

30207.name: Yura
30207.desc: Nagara-class light cruiser number four – Yura.

30207.name: We are Succubi?
30207.desc: Uh... I think these clothes are a bit too much... Commander, I... don't look out of place in these, do I...?

30208.name: Kinu
30208.desc: I'm Kinu. If you want this demon to do your bidding, then you'd better show me what you're capable of!

30208.name: New Year's Blade Demon
30208.desc: Grr! What are you here for? Speak up. ...Oh, you just wanted to take a tour of the club activities? Sorry 'bout that, I don't like getting disturbed in the middle of this kind of training.

30208.name: Token and Ghost
30208.desc: Well? I've still got one card in my hand. If you want to win, then show me everything you've got! I will not have you disrespect me just for wearing a silly costume!

30208.name: Kinu (Retrofit)
30208.desc: Retrofit complete... Look forward to commanding the might of the demon ascended. I shall not disappoint you!

30209.name: Abukuma
30209.desc: Sixth ship of the Nagara-class light cruisers, Abukuma.

30209.name: Abukuma (Retrofit)
30209.desc: Combat retrofit complete! First Torpedo Squadron flagship, Abukuma, ready to sortie any time!

30210.name: Mogami (Retrofit)
30210.desc: Are you sure this is a retrofit and not some weird hazing ritual? I look... Well, I suppose I do feel stronger. Guess I'll try to work a bit harder. Wouldn't hurt for you to look forward to it a little.

30211.name: Mikuma
30211.desc: Mogami-class heavy cruiser number two – Mikuma.

30211.name: Offerings of Floral Grace
30211.desc: Commander, may you and all our friends enjoy peace and good health... Alright, what did you think? That was a ceremonial dance I'd like to offer to everyone at the main event.

30212.name: Sendai
30212.desc: Sendai-class light cruiser number one – Sendai.

30212.name: Sendai (Retrofit)
30212.desc: Hmh. Guess I won't be needin' these bandages anymore. Commander, how about we find out how strong I've gotten... by having you take one of my punches?

30213.name: The Tactician's Vacation
30213.desc: Hmm? Is it unusual? Hah. Even I require a change of pace to clear my mind every so often. Commander, why don’t you come out and get some fresh air as well?

30213.name: The Gray Wolf's Ploy
30213.desc: "Where do you think you're going so early in the morning, Little Red Riding Hood?" ...Oh, if it isn't the Commander. This might be my own little whim, but I often find myself thinking the same way as this character... If you don't mind, I'd like to hear your feedback about my acting.

30213.name: Jintsuu (Retrofit)
30213.desc: Since I've gotten used to living with you, Commander, I've decided to be more laid-back after receiving my remodel. My dance? Hehe... I can't show that to just anyone so easily.

30214.name: Naka
30214.desc: Sendai-class light cruiser number three – Naka.

30214.name: Foxy Summer Surfer
30214.desc: Ahaha! Another big one's coming~! Phew~ that felt amazing~! Ah, Commander, let's hit the waves together, shall we?

30220.name: Agano
30220.desc: Agano-class light cruiser number one – Agano.

30220.name: Christmas Eve Tease
30220.desc: Even though I'm not really into this whole "Christmas" thing, if it means I get to toy around with your heart by wearing this cute outfit of mine, then I suppose I would be interested. Hehe~

30220.name: Dating Game?
30220.desc: "Oh my, you're also out for a stroll? Hehe, my name's Agano. And what might yours be?" ...Jeez, Commander, take this more seriously. According to the setting, we just met for the first time.

30220.name: Blue Butterfly's Confession
30220.desc: The blunt approach is not my style, but I cannot have Noshiro think I only inch my way to success... Oh, I was just talking to myself, Commander. Hehe, so anyway, would you mind being my partner for tonight's party?

30221.name: Noshiro
30221.desc: Agano-class light cruiser number two – Noshiro.

30221.name: Uncharted Festival Grounds?
30221.desc: Just as I thought, this is the perfect place for watching fireworks. You came here thinking that too, didn't you?

30221.name: Xanadu's Eventide
30221.desc: Commander, what are you standing around for? Did you also need a change of pace? That makes two of us— Come, there's nothing to be afraid of here.

30221.name: Fragrance of the Eastern Snow
30221.desc: Whew... Oh, are you cold by any chance? I have some hot tea for you if you'd like. If you want someone to chat with, I'd be glad to keep you company.

30221.name: Cozy Enclave
30221.desc: Why don't you unwind for a bit before you start reflecting on the day's happenings? I'm sure it'll be far more efficient that way.

30221.name: Hold the Ice
30221.desc: Welcom...?! What are you doing here? Wait, don't leave—I was just surprised, that's all... Well, what would you like to order?

30221.name: Unwinding in the Sunshine
30221.desc: ...Take that! Heehee... Ahaha! Phew... I know you don't like admitting defeat, but I got you pretty good there. I might have tried a bit too hard, but I'm pretty sure you were the one who told me to give it my all.

30221.name: A Tale of Two Lovers
30221.desc: Receiving everyone's blessings is truly a deeply moving experience. But for now, let's set everything else aside and partake of our sweet bliss. After all, you're not just a spectator anymore– we're in this ride together, hehe~

30223.name: Sakawa
30223.desc: Agano-class light cruiser number four – Sakawa.

30223.name: The Colors of Love
30223.desc: Welcome! Heehee, you came because you were just so keen to see me, am I right? Then I've got to make you feel real welcome♪

30301.name: Furutaka
30301.desc: First ship of the Furutaka-class heavy cruisers, Furutaka.

30301.name: Furutaka (Retrofit)
30301.desc: What's wrong, Commander? Why are you staring at me like that? My body? Yes, some things seem to have gotten bigger... Want to take a look?

30302.name: Kako
30302.desc: Second ship of Furutaka-class heavy cruisers, Kako.

30302.name: Kako (Retrofit)
30302.desc: Performance upgraded, improvements complete. This way I can finally... *cough* Oh, it's nothing, Commander. I must simply be more strict with you in the future. Are you ready for your psychological examination?

30303.name: Aoba
30303.desc: First ship of the Aoba-class heavy cruisers, Aoba.

30304.name: Kinugasa
30304.desc: Second ship of the Aoba-class heavy cruisers, Kinugasa.

30306.name: Chikuma
30306.desc: Tone-class heavy cruiser number two – Chikuma.

30307.name: Myoukou
30307.desc: First ship of the Myoukou-class heavy cruisers, Myoukou.

30308.name: Nachi
30308.desc: Second ship of the Myoukou-class heavy cruisers, Nachi.

30309.name: Ashigara
30309.desc: Myoukou-class heavy cruiser number three - Ashigara

30309.name: Brief Intermission
30309.desc: Phew... I finally managed to fix my dress... but I just can't seem to get used to it. Commander, how does my dress look? It's not strange, is it?

30309.name: Kaleidoscopic Summer
30309.desc: This whole "fashion coordination" concept is still a bit hard for me to wrap my head around, so I'm glad Nachi helped me pick out a swimsuit. Now, I just need to... Hey, Commander! Open your mouth! H-huh?! But this is what Nachi told me to do... is there some sort of problem?!

30310.name: Haguro
30310.desc: Myoukou-class heavy cruiser number four – Haguro.

30310.name: A Blessing in Disguise?
30310.desc: Ow! That freakin' stings... Can't believe I actually slipped on the stairs and hit my foot. Just how clumsy am I? ...Oh, Commander? Uh, welcome?

30310.name: Caught By Nightfall
30310.desc: H-hey, help me out! ...No, I didn't come in here for fun. When I finished my security duty last night, I got to thinking about how I was going to give you chocolate for Valentine's and fell asleep. When I woke up, I was stuffed in this thing...

30311.name: Takao
30311.desc: First ship of the Takao-class heavy cruisers, Takao.

30311.name: Beach Rhapsody
30311.desc: Commander, even I’ll get embarrassed if you keep staring at me like that... Eh? Why did I bring a volleyball? Did you not order me to bring it?

30311.name: The Lessons of Spring
30311.desc: Practicing writing is a type of training, isn't it? Commander... do you want to sit down and write with me?

30311.name: School Romanza
30311.desc: Hmm... school life, huh? It's a fairly fresh experience for me. Would it be fine to pin my hair up like this? What do you think, Commander?

30311.name: Full Throttle Charmer
30311.desc: Ugh... S-such shameless attire... If not for Atago saying that it would benefit me to experience different things...! It looks good on me?! I, I see...

30311.name: Sakura Hanami
30311.desc: Commander, I've been undertaking countless bride training sessions in order to prepare for this day. As your bride, I won't let you down.

30312.name: Atago
30312.desc: Second ship of the Takao-class heavy cruisers, Atago.

30312.name: Summer March
30312.desc: The warm breeze that gently wraps around your skin, and delicate footsteps across the white sand... isn’t this the essence of summer? Commander, what does summer mean to you?

30312.name: Hallmarks of Winter
30312.desc: Oh my, it's begun to snow. Commander, should we find a nice, quiet place to enjoy the view?

30312.name: School Traumerei
30312.desc: Student handbook, textbooks... twin guns, torpedoes... and what else... Huh? Commander, I'm just packing my bags for school... is there anything I'm missing?

30312.name: Stunning Speedster
30312.desc: So, you want big sister to be your "fleet queen"? You got it. But you'd better give it your all out there, or else I'll be upset with you!

30312.name: Lily-White Vow
30312.desc: Commander... Ahh, from now on, shouldn't I call you "darling?" Come and hold my hand... Ah, at times like these, I just can't help but to want to eat you up, dar~ling~

30313.name: Maya
30313.desc: Third ship of the Takao-class heavy cruisers, Maya.

30314.name: Choukai
30314.desc: Takao-class heavy cruiser number four – Choukai.

30314.name: Tidy Store, Tidy Mind
30314.desc: There, that's it for the entrance... Oh welcome, Commander! I've been cleaning, so give me a moment... I'll be right with you!

30317.name: Suzuya
30317.desc: Mogami-class heavy cruiser number three – Suzuya.

30318.name: Kumano
30318.desc: Mogami-class heavy cruiser number four – Kumano.

30318.name: Fancy Waves
30318.desc: It's time for Kumano's sexy swimsuit debut~! Just kidding~☆ Hey Commander, just where~ are~ you~ staring~? Ahaha~♡

30318.name: PJ Poker Party
30318.desc: Now it's your turn, Commander! Which one's it gonna be~? You suuuure you wanna pick this card? ...I hear you, Suzuya! Stop tellin' the Commander what the cards are!

30318.name: One Thousand and One Nights' Wishes
30318.desc: Tadah! Get a load of my... dancer outfit! So, whaddya think? Ahaha~♡ Hey, Commander, where are those eyes wandering? Did ya see something ya like?

30401.name: Kongou
30401.desc: Kongou-class fast battleship number one – Kongou.

30401.name: The Beauties of Nature
30401.desc: We must fully live in the present, whether during work or during leisure - this is my mantra. Commander, shall we go for an outing together?

30401.name: Hospital Talent
30401.desc: "Celebrity Endorsement of the Port Medical Facilities"... Hehehe, you've made a wise decision picking me. Commander, I can leave the ad shoot to you, right?

30401.name: Breezy Commute
30401.desc: It would be a shame to pass on this lovely weather, Commander. Why have a dull commute by train when you can enjoy a leisurely bicycle ride in the sunlight, hm? Heehee♪

30402.name: Hiei
30402.desc: Kongou-class fast battleship number two – Hiei.

30402.name: Moonlit Cruise
30402.desc: Look how late it is... Commander, shall we embark on a dreamy voyage together?

30402.name: Fragrant Red Plum
30402.desc: I have to admit, these qipaos from the Dragon Empery are quite elegant... I might sound arrogant saying this, but I feel like this outfit really brings out my charm. Hehe, wouldn't you agree, Commander?

30402.name: Beauty of the White Sands
30402.desc: We're headed for the white sands of the beach today. We all could use a breather every now and then, so let's just enjoy the sea breeze today. Hehe~

30403.name: Haruna
30403.desc: Kongou-class fast battleship number four – Haruna.

30403.name: Free Time Before Class
30403.desc: I think it's fine to enjoy school life once in a while... Hm? You wanna know what I'm listening to? Sure, if you're okay with just one earbud.

30403.name: Scarlet Innocence
30403.desc: I guess that looks right... Since Kongou chose this for me, I must trust her judgment... Um, C-Commander, would you mind helping me out? ...It's a bit hard to walk in this outfit...

30403.name: The Elegant Lotus
30403.desc: "My dear Commander, is this dress that my sisters tailored for me to your liking?" ...Okay, no, I can't do polite Hiei-speak like she can... So, anyway, h-how do I look?

30404.name: Kirishima
30404.desc: Kongou-class fast battleship number four – Kirishima.

30404.name: After-School Cannon Time
30404.desc: Commander, enjoying school life is all fine and well, but we must not forget our duty... That said, what missions are waiting for us today?

30404.name: Summery Audacity
30404.desc: Being in front of my sisters in this outfit is one thing, but it really is embarrassing to be wearing it in front of you, Commander. Um... ahem! What do you think? Since you're here, want to walk down to the beach together?

30404.name: Casual Dazzle
30404.desc: "Commander, bad luck for you, but you're just going to become another notch on my blade." Haha, just kidding, it's a joke! So, what do you think? My New Year's attire is pretty snazzy, isn't it?

30404.name: Graceful Ink Incense
30404.desc: The Lunar New Year is known for its hustle and bustle, but it's nice to just sit down with a brush and take in the smell of ink. Hey Commander, got any words you want to see rendered in calligraphy?

30405.name: Amagi
30405.desc: 1st Ship of the Amagi-class Battlecruisers, Amagi

30405.name: Wending Waters, Serene Lotus
30405.desc: Commander, are you here to pay me a visit? ...Ah, there is no need to be concerned about me. I made a promise to both you and Akagi that I would be mindful of my health.

30406.name: Hiei-chan
30406.desc: Fast Battleship, second ship of the Kongou-class Hiei.

30407.name: Amagi-chan
30407.desc: 1st Ship of the Amagi-class Battlecruisers, Amagi

30501.name: Fusou
30501.desc: First ship of the Fusou-class battleships, Fusou.

30501.name: The Celebration of Spring
30501.desc: Yamashiro said always dressing like a witch can be a bit old-fashioned, so she gave me a new outfit. That kid... Do you think it looks good on me, Commander?

30501.name: Perfect Partner?
30501.desc: Changing into leisure clothes, and waiting for the return of my beloved... Milord, I too have changed since meeting you.

30501.name: Fusou (Retrofit)
30501.desc: Milord! Thank you~ Not just for the retrofit, but for many many things. Hehe, it was the greatest of fortune for me and Yamashiro to meet you.

30502.name: Yamashiro
30502.desc: Second ship of the Fusou-class battleships, Yamashiro.

30502.name: Summer Offensive?
30502.desc: It’s just not summer without beach volleyball! Ah... Milord, you’re not playing? But I went through all this effort to pick out a swimsuit...

30502.name: Holiday Offensive
30502.desc: Merry Christmas! Milord, milord, how do I look? Is my Christmas outfit pretty? Ehehe~ Big sis also praised me today!

30502.name: Dressy Black Cat
30502.desc: Fusou told me that I have to wear a Western-style dress to the banquet, so she got one for me! Milord, Milord, isn't this dress pretty?

30502.name: Sales Clerk Offensive?!
30502.desc: Milord, Milord, welcome to the store! Yamashiro is a sales clerk today! Mhm, I'll do my best!

30502.name: Vacation Offensive!
30502.desc: Woah, even the air tastes totally different at this vacation spot! Milord, Milord, um, Akashi asked me to bottle up some of the air here for her! Want to give me a hand?

30502.name: Street Corner Offensive!
30502.desc: Uwaah! M-Milord?! I'm so, so sorry... You didn't get hurt, did you? Um... This is my school uniform. Fusou tailored it for me, hehe~ ... Awawa! I should head off to class now! See you later!

30502.name: Bridal Attack!
30502.desc: Milord, Milord, I've finished changing! What do you think, what do you think? Milord, do you like Yamashiro's dress~?

30502.name: Yamashiro (Retrofit)
30502.desc: Milord! I can do anything now~ bombardment or aerial strikes! So, the thing is, you can totally count on me, much much more, Milord! Milord~!

30503.name: Ise
30503.desc: First ship of the Ise-class battleships, Ise.

30503.name: Ise (Retrofit)
30503.desc: Planes: check! Main guns: check! Nobody can stop me now! Let's sortie right now, Commander! I'm fired up and wanna wreak some havoc on the battlefield!

30504.name: Hyuuga
30504.desc: Second ship of the Ise-class battleships, Hyuuga.

30504.name: Hyuuga (Retrofit)
30504.desc: Aviation battleship Hyuuga, sporting new powers, reporting in! Rest easy, Commander, I'll show you my true post-retrofit power!

30505.name: Great Fox's Respite
30505.desc: I shall be hosting the commander today. Manjuus, I beseech you to help me look my best. I am... *yawn* a bit sleepy... Urghh... what is that ruckus out there? C-Commander! When did you arrive?

30505.name: Guardian Fox's Shining Furisode
30505.desc: Perfect, you have arrived. As long as you are here, the usual moon-watching will prove to be much more enjoyable... Why don't you stay here today and rest for a while?

30505.name: Guardian Fox's Vacation
30505.desc: I heard that it is custom to play a "sport" at this kind of event, involving throwing pillows at others. Heheh, then I shall put the might of the Big Seven on display!

30505.name: Guardian Fox's Procession
30505.desc: Though this is a splendorous dress befitting the occasion, it is too different from my usual attire... Mutsu and Mikasa have nothing but praise for it? If you say so, then perhaps... I can take your word. Hehe.

30505.name: Great Fox's White Gown
30505.desc: It may be presumptuous of me, but please take care of me from now on... Is that acceptable? S-Somehow, it feels a little embarrassing... Ahaha...

30506.name: Warring States Warship
30506.desc: Commander, check it out! "Nothing can stop me!" Urakaze made it for me! Now I can play warring states with her! Heheh, you should know I'm a force to be reckoned with! Can't you come play with us? Why?

30506.name: A Maid's Mis-service?
30506.desc: Hmh? If fah foo, Fummamuh? ...*gulp*. I'm not lazing around! I'm just checking on the pastries that just came in! What are you doing here anyway? To "taste-test?" Or is there something wrong with the pastries? Why?

30508.name: Hometown Zest
30508.desc: An inspection? ...You're awfully gung-ho about your work considering how hot it is outside... Surely you wouldn't have some sort of ulterior motive?

30510.name: Violet Moonglow
30510.desc: "Welcome back, Master." Rather, that's what all the children at the café were saying to you when they greeted you at the door. Hehe, is this some new custom?

30511.name: Style of the Sakura Capital
30511.desc: I found quite the nostalgic outfit when I was cleaning my wardrobe. Let's see... "Prepare to come with me on a new journey!" How do I look, Commander?

30511.name: Blossom-Viewing Season
30511.desc: It's about time for the flowers to bloom once more. Alas, how the time flies by... Ahem, Commander, let's see, would you like to go blossom-viewing with me?

30511.name: Reverence for Rest and Relaxation
30511.desc: Even I like to dress down and unwind from time to time. Oh? This is new and exciting for you? Well, you are welcome to come see more of it from now on! Hahaha!

30511.name: A Romantic Respite
30511.desc: Welcome to the Sakura Empire's pop-up café... Oh, Commander! Everyone's waiting for you. Now get your butt in here and experience the full extent of our fleet's hospitality! Don't be nervous, now! Hahaha!

30511.name: Untarnished Splendor
30511.desc: I, battleship Mikasa, from now until eternity, pledge to you my undying love and devotion. May we help each other, encourage each other, and walk side-by-side on the same path. I hope to meet your expectations, as unworthy as I may be.

30512.name: Poolside Persuasion
30512.desc: Refreshing drinks, delicious food, warm sunshine... and a pool to beat the heat? Heh, isn't this the essence of summer?

30514.name: Suruga
30514.desc: Battleship Suruga, reporting for duty. It would seem that some threads of fate connect me to this port... No, don't mind my rambling. Please disregard that.

30514.name: Hundred Flowers' Auspice
30514.desc: Good morning, Commander. Everyone else seems to be dressed up on this day of celebration, so this shouldn't be a problem, right?

30514.name: Straightfaced Model Student
30514.desc: Oh. Fancy meeting you here... Walk to school together? Uh, sure! I know the way, so please just follow me.

30514.name: Uneventful Holiday Greetings
30514.desc: This should do it. With how unremarkable my present is, I doubt it'll make any waves when the... Ack! Commander?! Why are you here?!

30601.name: Hiyou
30601.desc: Hiyou-class aircraft carrier number one – Hiyou.

30602.name: Junyou
30602.desc: Hiyou-class aircraft carrier number two – Junyou.

30603.name: The Dream of the Autumn Pillow
30603.desc: While everyone slips into sweet dreams from the night's festivities, the sound of gossamer sliding off of smooth skin reaches your ears... Hehe, would you like to spend this night under the stars with me, Master~?

30605.name: Shouhou
30605.desc: First ship of the Shouhou-class aircraft carriers, Shouhou.

30605.name: Patrolling Witch
30605.desc: Waaaah! My candy! Candy is spillin’ everywhere! ...Wh-why are y’all chasin’ me? Commander, help me catch the pumpkin!

30605.name: Shouhou (Retrofit)
30605.desc: Commander, how do I look now that I've grown up? Are ya fallin' in love with me already? Mhm, ye definitely are~

30606.name: Slacking Samurai
30606.desc: *yawn*... Finally, a good night's rest... Now, to pick up where I left off on that RPG... M-m-m-milord, why are you here?! I wasn't slacking off or anything, I w-w-was just... Ughh....

30606.name: Dragon Hunter: Ryuujou's Rise
30606.desc: All right! Steady! Steadyyy! Gottem! Hahahah! Now I'll– M-Milord?! I-I'm just, umm... enjoying an after-school break!

30607.name: Firebird's New Year Dance
30607.desc: Commander, everyone seems to be busy with end-of-year preparations. If there is anything I can do to help, please let me know.

30608.name: Summer Shine
30608.desc: An order of coconut milk... and grilled sausage. Mm, that should do it. ...Hm? Commander? Are you here to place an order, or to get away from the heat?

30608.name: Mosaic of Blending Colors
30608.desc: I had this outfit custom-made just for today... Do you like it, Commander? Um, that's good then... (*whispers*) Booyah.

30609.name: Shimmering Surf
30609.desc: Hehe~ If you don't have any other plans, then your only task... is to enjoy a holiday by the sea! Commander, have you switched into vacation mode yet?

30701.name: Paradise Amaryllis
30701.desc: "When you gaze long into the abyss, the abyss also gazes into you." Commander, please do not forget that when you gaze at Akagi~ *giggles*

30701.name: Plum and Snow
30701.desc: Commander will always remain by Akagi's side... Right, "Gods?" Of course... Akagi will deal with the pests.... Ahaha...

30701.name: Ruby-Laced Beauty
30701.desc: Commander, I've been waiting for you~ What a sinful one you are, to tempt Akagi like this for so long... But at long last, nobody will ever get between us again...♡

30701.name: Dawn-Phoenix's Summons
30701.desc: This banquet is my present to you... and your attendance is the greatest reward I could hope for~ Indeed, I shall not grant you leave tonight until you pass out. Ehehe... Ahahaha~♡

30701.name: Deep Crimson Poppy
30701.desc: We should send out even more invites... This is the best way to rid ourselves of those pesky vixens all at once!

30702.name: Everlasting Killing Stone
30702.desc: "You only live once?" Where have I heard that saying before... Commander, are you getting excited?

30702.name: White Fox's New Year
30702.desc: One must wear appropriate attire for the New Year. What do you think, Commander? Let me hear your opinion.

30702.name: Exalted White Wings
30702.desc: This statue seems to have been inspired by the teachings of the Iris Orthodoxy. Though I am unfamiliar with this kind of art, gazing upon such majesty... fills one with a sense of piety. Commander, can you feel it as well?

30702.name: Gentle Blossom's Sigh
30702.desc: I never thought you'd end up taking such a long trip with me just to pick up a dress... Though I'm worried about leaving my sister behind at port, I suppose I should take your advice and relax a bit.

30702.name: Dusk-Simurgh's Vigil
30702.desc: What are you doing up here?! Oh, it's you. I thought you went to see my sister? ...You needed a breath of fresh air? That's all fine, but you should return to my sister soon before she does something mad.

30702.name: Sacred Blue Lily
30702.desc: "To hold one's hand and grow old together with him"... If it is to be with you, then it won't so bad.

30703.name: The Crane Amidst the Pines
30703.desc: I tried wearing something a bit different from usual, but I'm not sure it suits me... Commander, what do you think?

30703.name: The Counselor Girl
30703.desc: Counselor girl Souryuu! Remedy the school atmosphere and correct your learning attitude, and...well, in short, I protect the discipline of the school.

30703.name: Souryuu (Retrofit)
30703.desc: If I can become stronger through this... Commander, what are you staring at? Don't you still have work to do?

30704.name: After School Bullies
30704.desc: Without girl bullies, there would be no disciplinary girl. So...before sister catches me, let’s cause some mischief at school.

30704.name: Hiryuu (Retrofit)
30704.desc: Retrofit complete! Aircraft Carrier Hiryuu, reporting for duty! Hahaha! I finally got the chance to use that line! I'll be counting on you once more!

30705.name: Shoukaku
30705.desc: First ship of the Shoukaku-class aircraft carriers, Shoukaku.

30705.name: The Crane that Dances With the Wind
30705.desc: I prepared this outfit just for the occasion, so... Commander, you're not going to disappoint me, are you? Hehe~♪

30705.name: Sororal Wings
30705.desc: Hehe, this kind of work is a simple matter for me. Commander, please look forward to my performance~

30706.name: Zuikaku
30706.desc: Second ship of the Shoukaku-class aircraft carriers, Zuikaku.

30706.name: Ceremonial Crane
30706.desc: New Elite 1st CarDiv, Zuikaku, reporting for duty! Ahh, I've always wanted to give such a cool introduction! Shoukaku would definitely make fun of me if she heard it, but I wanted to try it while everyone is in a festive mood... Commander, what'd you think?

30706.name: The Wind's True Name
30706.desc: Commander, I volunteered to take this job in order to help you out, but this outfit... did it always require such a high degree of exposure...?

30707.name: Forbidden Fruit
30707.desc: You're taking so long to dress yourself, my Commander. Are you struggling to find something to match my dress? Hehe, it doesn't matter what you wear, you're always perfect to me♡

30707.name: Phoenix's Spring Song
30707.desc: Hehehe, I let Christmas and New Year's slip right by me, that I might use the Dragon Empery's Lunar New Year to capture my Commander's attentions... Oh, My Commander, won't you please enjoy the show I've prepared for you♡

30707.name: Enraptured Companion
30707.desc: Do I make a nice race queen, my Commander...? Hehe. With these proportions, and my fantastic outfit~♡ The others couldn't hope to compare with me!

30707.name: Sweet Time After School
30707.desc: Ehehe~ There is no greater bliss than being with you after classes are over, my Commander~ The kitty here seems to agree♡

30707.name: Temptation on the Sea Breeze
30707.desc: My Commander~ Do you like the location that I've chosen~? We have the entire evening to ourselves, free from the disturbance of anyone else...! Ahhh, my heart is throbbing even more vigorously than the ocean's waves~♡

30708.name: Dreams of the Hazy Moon
30708.desc: The moonlight dims beneath hazy clouds, and the lights of the night sky begin to shine... The moon, and this sake, are both intoxicating... Will you not enjoy this fine evening with me...?

30708.name: Moonlit Chrome
30708.desc: Hnnh... Such clamors of merriment... Would this one be welcome amidst these festivities? Alas... If you so desire, how can this one refuse...?

30710.name: Akagi μ
30710.desc: With the magicks of the Sakura Empire, changing my form like this is a trifle... Hehehe, Commander? Does this Akagi please you?

30711.name: Taihou μ
30711.desc: With these clothes, and upon this stage... Ahaha... Ahahaha... Fate has ordained that my Commander shall fall for me here... Commander, please listen to the song of my love until the very end~♡

30712.name: Night-Illuminating Festival
30712.desc: It's– summer– festival– time–!! Uhh, well, maybe it's a bit too late for a "summer" festival, so maybe a regular festival is fine? Well, the important thing is that you have lots of fun, Commander! Because I sure as heck will!

30801.name: Departure's Gentle Breeze
30801.desc: Aww, do I have to go to school? ... Oh, Commander! Are you here to see me off?

30801.name: Pillowy Paradise
30801.desc: So sleepy... Hey, Commandeeer? Do you wanna nap with me and my torpedo?

30801.name: Blossoming Bunny
30801.desc: I thought I'd try on this bunny costume! Hehehe, do you like it? If you think it's cute, I wanna hear you say it~

30802.name: Deep-Sea Rabbit
30802.desc: Many secrets lie at the bottom of the ocean! Commander, let's go looking for them next time! It'll be like a field trip~ Heheh!

30802.name: Shortly Before the Fireworks
30802.desc: Commander, are you also waiting for the fireworks to start? There's still some time, so let's have a little chat!

30804.name: Coral Reef Bunny
30804.desc: Hi there, Commander. Oh, this outfit? I'll be wearing it to school today. By the way, did you want to come sit in on my class?

30804.name: Sweet Wine of Celebration
30804.desc: Commander, Happy Lunar New Year. Would you like some sweet wine to celebrate? Oh, be careful not to drink too much~

30805.name: I-56
30805.desc: Type B3 Mod. 2 cruiser submarine – I-56.

30805.name: Wallflower in the Corner
30805.desc: School... is pretty nice. I can quietly stay in this corner and mind my own business...

30806.name: Festive Mood!
30806.desc: I look different from usual? That's obvious, isn't it... All right, all right, I was just giving you a hard time. We're at a festival, so we might as well enjoy ourselves!

31201.name: Akashi
31201.desc:
Repair ship Akashi
<color=#fad545>Can be built after unlocking

31201.name: Akashi's in the Red, Nya!
31201.desc: Commander, how does Akashi's new outfit look, nya? Isn't it cute? If you like it, then put a ring on it. I mean, everyone's gone out to play... if you don't help empty my inventory, I'll go broke, nya!

31201.name: The Black Cat Cometh!
31201.desc: Heheh, this is what I've been saving up for, nya~♪ A special dress that combines Gothic fashion with Sakura charm! Commander, how about those gems, nya?

31201.name: Welcome to AzurCon!
31201.desc: Ohh, it's Commander, nya. Have you come to buy Akashi's new work, nya? Today's a holiday, so go ahead and enjoy yourself, nya~

31201.name: Welcome to Sofmap!
31201.desc: Hehehe, come on in, nya! Can I help you find something, nya? Your genial and knowledgeable staff, Akashi, will gladly provide her detailed recommendations, nya!

31201.name: White Cat's Repayment
31201.desc: Commander, because of your continued patronage of my shop, I have no choice but to return the favor with my body, nya~! ...Just kidding, nya. Having that said, I really do love you, Commander. Even more than I love gems, nya~

31701.name: I-13
31701.desc: Type A Mod. 2 cruiser submarine – I-13.

31901.name: Hot Springs Relaxation
31901.desc: Ack... Owww... My apologies, Commander, I seem to have slipped on something... At times, it's hard to notice things I'm about to step on... Ugh...

31901.name: Maid for Mayhem
31901.desc: Hyah?! U-Umm, I can't get out... Oh, Commander?! I'm sorry! I tripped while I was cleaning, and I ended up stuck in here! Umm... What do I do now...

39901.name: Winter Sylph's Reverie
39901.desc: Milord, it's starting to snow... If it suits you, please take shelter under Ibuki's umbrella.
