39901.name: Snow on the Wind
39901.desc: This is my first time wearing Western clothes... Um, Milord! Does this outfit... suit Ibuki well...?

39901.name: Arrival of Spring
39901.desc: The Dragon Empery's "Spring Festival" is... filled with fun, liveliness, and pure jubilation. I can feel my true feelings welling up... Maybe, an environment like this would suit me pretty well...

39901.name: Tranquil Sunya
39901.desc: I'm glad you've returned, Milord. I've changed my attire in order to better carry out your order–for us to "relax together." Now then... could you please instruct me on how to proceed?

39902.name: Izumo's Thousand Cherry Trees
39902.desc: You'd like to see my classical dance? Your tastes are quite refined, Commander... In that case, I'll show you the finest performance in the land!

39903.name: Celebration Conquest!
39903.desc: All the preparations are now complete... Commander, let us sally forth and conquer these festival grounds! ...But before that, can we get something to eat first?

39903.name: Night of Doves and Magic
39903.desc: Mm, preparations complete. If I keep it up, the production will surely be a great success. The doves have been on their best behavior too. Commander, what do you think about Kitakaze's magic show?

39904.name: Soft Voice of Spring
39904.desc: Commander? Oh, I haven't quite finished changing. My hair still needs work... Sorry, would you mind waiting a bit longer?

39904.name: Lily-White Longing
39904.desc: I must be dreaming, to be able to don this white veil... Haha, though, what's more important is our life together afterwards! Commander, please look forward to the rich fruit of my bridal training~

39905.name: Slice, Dice, and Serve
39905.desc: All righty, one freshly-sliced plate of sashimi coming right up! ...Huh? I'm coming across too aggressive? Even after I went through all this trouble for you, you still have something to nitpick about? ...Well, whatever. Enjoy your meal!

40101.name: "Rebellious" Top Student
40101.desc: Because she’s the Z1, her results will of course be NO.1! Hehe, no matter where she goes, Z1-sama will always be the best!

40101.name: Z1 (Retrofit)
40101.desc: Hmm... So this is a retrofit, huh? Not bad! Rejoice once more, Commander, for no task or enemy is too daunting for the new and improved Z1!

40102.name: High-Rise, High-Style
40102.desc: Commander, I do wonder if your order to "come dressed in new clothes" was simply your way of saying "I want to see you in a casual outfit." No matter the case, I'm happy to oblige.

40102.name: Of Koi and Evening Hues
40102.desc: Being able to see you all flabbergasted makes changing into this outfit worth it. Are you going to keep standing there like a scarecrow? Come over here~ Who knows, we might even be able to see the fireworks from this spot.

40116.name: Guaranteed Grand Slam!
40116.desc: Heh heh! Count your lucky stars, Commander, because you're just in time – to witness the one-and-only Z16 knock this thing right outta the ballpark!

40123.name: Philosophy Sensei
40123.desc: This is going to be on the exam! If you don't take thorough notes, I am going to punish you!

40123.name: Breezy Doubles
40123.desc: Haiyaaah! It's up to you, Ayanami! Oh, Commander! Are you actually keeping score? We might not be having a serious match, but that's no excuse for you to stand around and do nothing.

40123.name: Perfect Smile?
40123.desc: Welcome! A table for one today? Um... Commander, my smile doesn’t look stiff... right?

40123.name: The Banquet's Honor Student
40123.desc: Oh, good evening, Commander. I was just looking for Javelin and the others... Say, would you like to keep me company for a bit?

40123.name: Café Trainee @New Base
40123.desc: Hi, welcome! How may I serve y– It's you, Commander?! Err, well, I'm working as a trainee at this Sakura Empire-style café, you see... What do you think of this outfit?

40123.name: Serious Idol @Acting Manager?!
40123.desc: Jeez... Javelin's got what it takes, but I'm really concerned about Laffey and Ayanami. Oh well, I guess it's up to me to manage them... Commander, please don't forget to support me too.

40123.name: The Eyecatch in the Rye?
40123.desc: Commander, please help hold onto the ladder. I've almost got the book... Just a little more... All right... C-Commander?! Please don't look up!

40123.name: Schwarze Hochzeit
40123.desc: Whew... Sorry to keep you waiting. I was having a hard time deciding which outfit to wear... Ah, um... how do I look?

40123.name: Z23 (Retrofit)
40123.desc: My efficiency should be upgraded along with my performance. Paperwork, battle plans... I can handle them all! Commander, be prepared, we’ll be very busy~

40123.name: Keeper of the Comf-Fort
40123.desc: *sigh*... Taking care of Meowfficers is more work than you'd think... They're awfully needy for support units. Commander, make absolute sure you don't turn out like them.

40123.name: Upgrade Failure?!
40123.desc: N-no way... I lost the gear I worked so hard for because the upgrade failed, and now I'm completely out of gold... Ugh, I'm going to have to go farm the dungeon all over again...

40124.name: Festival-going Fiend
40124.desc: Come, human! The rite of festivities is upon us! Come hither, and let us revel in this foreign holiday together!

40124.name: The Devil on the Court
40124.desc: Heh heh... As expected, you couldn't even last for a second! Winning too easily takes all the fun out of it... You, the mortal over there, I'll give you the honor of being my next opponent!

40125.name: Hot Summer's Cool Breeze
40125.desc: Even at the beach, we cannot afford to be careless! Commander, have you adequately prepared for today's activities?

40126.name: Sharing is Caring
40126.desc: Commander, welcome to my pad! Ah, give me a sec, let me go grab all the snacks and drinks and games!

40128.name: New Year Smorgasbord!
40128.desc: Commander, Happy New Year! Is there anything you'd like to do on New Year's Day? Say, why don't we try doing all of that stuff, all at once~?

40128.name: Sylvan Celebration
40128.desc: Prosit, Commander! I think these wild animals were attracted by the champagne's aroma. But they're well-behaved and like being petted. Do you want to be petted too, Commander?

40135.name: Projekt Kirschblüte
40135.desc: Commander, and all my fellow friends of the fleet, Happy New Year's! This time, your favorite idol Z35 will be presenting a brand new Sakura-themed collaboration, "Projekt Kirschblüte!" Everyone, thank you for your continued support!

40146.name: Her First Summer
40146.desc: The bustling beach, clamoring with waves of joyfulness... experiencing this kind of summer is a first for me, but I don't dislike it...

40146.name: Girls' Relay
40146.desc: Through the sweat and tears, striving for your goals. Rejoice in victory, sink within defeat... How fascinating, this "sports meet" may be.

40146.name: Star-Lit★Chocolate
40146.desc: Dancing beams of light, shimmering on-stage; uplifted voices, joined as one by song... Upon this unknown stage, my heart doth flutter... Yet this sensation, is quite refreshing.

40146.name: Jianzhi Fantasia
40146.desc: "Jianzhi," the art of breathing life into works of cut paper... is a world beyond my imagination. If these decorations are said to usher in blessings... are they akin to a coat-of-arms or a holy seal?

40146.name: Chronicles of the Dust Wars
40146.desc: Cast your eyes upon this bit of dust. As I was entrusted with the cleaning, I shall not allow this dust to remain. Will you also join me in this battle?

40203.name: Köln (Retrofit)
40203.desc: Hmm... I feel like I can work even more efficiently than before. Commander, please rest assured, I will never betray your expectations.

40204.name: Leipzig
40204.desc:
Leipzig-class light cruiser, Leipzig.
<color=#fad545>Can be built after unlocking

40204.name: Storefront Training
40204.desc: Commander, ah, um... We have all new items on the menu, and they're on sale for a limited time only... P-please give them a try! Phew... Th-thank goodness, I managed to not flub it...

40204.name: Leipzig (Retrofit)
40204.desc: I feel like Fishy is a lot more capable than before, but I don't feel much different... M-maybe Fishy was the one to get a retrofit instead of me?!

40205.name: Spring Wanderer
40205.desc: Since you so readily accepted my invitation to go on a vacation together, you must be planning to... Ahh, what I meant is, we can leave at any time if you're ready...!

40206.name: Cat Café Cleanup
40206.desc: You little...! Look what a damn mess you made! And I'm the one who's gotta clean it up now! ...Oh. Perfect timing, Commander. Could use a hand with the floor here, after what this little turd did.

40206.name: Gone Fishing
40206.desc: Here's an idea – how 'bout putting down the camera and actually enjoyin' the open sea? I'll move the swim ring so you can chill in the breeze with me!

40207.name: White-Black Partita
40207.desc: Raise your head, my darling human. O lost soul, you have three options – become Emden's meal, become Emden's prisoner... "Or become Emden's vassal. Our vassal♥"

40207.name: Moonsilver Union
40207.desc: Welcome, my darling human. Are you looking for something? If it is Emden you seek, you have already found her. "We, Emden, are before your very eyes."

40208.name: The Throne of Misfortune
40208.desc: As the mistress of this manor, I c-command thee to kneel... No, of course. I mean, what authority do I have to issue commands? I'm better suited to be a maid than a mistress...

40208.name: Sleepless Night's Wishes
40208.desc: Are you also having trouble sleeping, Commander? I-I thought so... It must be because I was praying for you to have sweet dreams... Look what I've done – now, neither of us can fall asleep... Urgh...

40301.name: Admiral Hipper
40301.desc: Admiral Hipper-class Heavy Cruiser, Admiral Hipper

40301.name: Sunshine by the Hot Spring
40301.desc: W-well? Does this kimono look good on me? ...R-really? Duh, I know it looks GREAT on me! Who really cares what you think... C-can't be me... No, I didn't say anything!

40302.name: High-Altitude Head Over Heels
40302.desc: Heheheh☆ You're lagging behind, Commander! Pick up the pace or you'll be left behind! Just kidding~ I'll slow down for you so we can stick together!

40303.name: Prinz Eugen
40303.desc: Admiral Hipper-class Heavy Cruiser, Prinz Eugen

40303.name: Unfading Smile
40303.desc: Relaxing on a float, gently licking my lips... is this really the most popular photo pose for the beach? Wales, you’re not teasing me again, are you?

40303.name: Profusion of Flowers
40303.desc: So this is the Sakura Empire's New Year? Hehe, how interesting~ Commander, since it's the New Year, why don't you put aside all those papers and have a drink with me?

40303.name: Cordial Cornflower
40303.desc: ... Huh? Commander, is that you? Me, drunk? No way... *hic*... If I was, Commander, then what are you planning to do to me? Hehe...

40303.name: Final Lap
40303.desc: Viel Glück~ Are you having a good time, Commander? Just know that the only person I'm cheering for... is you~

40303.name: Kindred Evening Spirits
40303.desc: Guten Abend~ So, what do you think? Pretty great view, right? Hehe, I was talking about the night scenery outside, you know~?

40303.name: Symphonic Fate
40303.desc: If fate brought us together, then it has my thanks… I look forward to our future together~

40304.name: Dark Demon Princess
40304.desc: For a servant, your eyes are good... *coughs*... I'm an Ironblood Princess, the Queen of Night, Deutschland! Servant? No. I am the first of my family. Come, kiss the ring of royalty!

40304.name: Service Time?!
40304.desc: One must not neglect sunscreen during the summer... Plebeian, if you wish to serve your master, prostrate yourself and yell "I beg of you, Queen Deutschland" three times, and I might consider giving you an opportunity. Ahahaha~

40304.name: Demon Princess' Dark Hour Banquet
40304.desc: I seem pleased? Of course I am. Why wouldn't I be when my sweet little sister will be joining us at the party? Now shape up and entertain your master, you lowly animal! Ahahahaha!

40304.name: Lantern-Lit Ruler
40304.desc: Why are so many people out and about during a holiday? ...That's it! Lowly animal, was it your idea to prepare all this to surprise me...?! Heh... Hehe, that's right, don't you dare disappoint me!

40305.name: Admiral Graf Spee
40305.desc: Deutschland-class armored cruiser number three – Admiral Graf Spee.

40305.name: Girl's Sunday
40305.desc: I sailed alone, fought alone, and then I was sunk while being alone. Now I found a new beginning... Hmm? Commander, you've been staring and laughing at me since the beginning… do you want to eat this?

40305.name: Peaceful Daily Life
40305.desc: I never dreamt that I'd be able to don this outfit and live a normal, peaceful life... Thank you, Commander...

40305.name: A Novel Anniversary
40305.desc: It's so fancy, so formal... Is this a "party"? I'm not sure I'll be able to fit in... But if you'll go with me, Commander, I'll give it a try!

40305.name: World's♥Cutest
40305.desc: My sister just wouldn't stop bugging me, so I finally caved and agreed to do this... Anyways, all I have to do is get up on stage and sing, right?

40307.name: Admiral Hipper μ
40307.desc: Huh? Why are you staring at me like I'm some weirdo? I'll have you know, it's not like I wanted to do this or anything!

40308.name: Roon μ
40308.desc: Heavy cruiser Roon, reporting for idol activities and associated experimental equipment testing. Today, we fight not with fire and sword, but with the power of song.

40309.name: Fireworks and Tapestries
40309.desc: Phew... Changing into these clothes took quite a long time~ So, how does it look? A fine mixing of different cultures, wouldn't you agree? Ahaha, Happy New Year, Commander!

40309.name: Rabbit on Watch
40309.desc: *ptwee*! Remember: safety first! Commander, you've got to do your stretches before going in the pool! Be thorough, or I'll get mad at you!

40309.name: Secret Boss o' the Underworld?
40309.desc: Listen up, Commander! I'm the one in charge of this school's seedy underbelly here at this port, so you'd better do what I tell you to! In return, I'll offer you my protection! Ahaha~♪

40310.name: After-Hours Service
40310.desc: Zzz... Huh? Did I doze off? I just meant to rest my eyes for a sec after closing up, but look how long I slept... Hang on, why are you still here, Commander?

40311.name: Breaker under the Blood Moon
40311.desc: "Foolish, pitiable creature. Kneel before your Goddess!" Heehee! Hahahah, ahahahaha♥ You're the Commander, silly. You don't need to play along unless you want to.

40312.name: Little Prinz Eugen
40312.desc: Admiral Hipper-class heavy cruiser – Prinz Eugen.

40313.name: Little Spee
40313.desc: Deutschland-class armored cruiser – Admiral Graf Spee.

40401.name: Panther und Pflaume
40401.desc: A festival, huh? Going for days without fighting is boring, not to mention not my style. C'mon, Commander, isn't there *something* exciting I can do during this "Lunar New Year" festival?

40402.name: Nightmarish Succubus
40402.desc: These Halloween festivities are quite interesting, in a good way. Getting dressed up in these costumes isn't such a bad experience either. Commander, what do you think of my costume?

40403.name: Heir of the Vampire Killer
40403.desc: There it is – Dracula's Castle, brought into this world by chaos itself... On my honor, I swear I will put an end to the divine bloodline!

40403.name: Floral Liberation
40403.desc: How do I look, Commandant? I thought you may like seeing me in a dress, however I don't know if this is what you desired or not...

40404.name: Everlasting Blood Banquet
40404.desc: "Have you come to accept your fate, human? Heehee~" ...Don't just stand there, Commander. Say something!

40404.name: Steaming-Hot Treat
40404.desc: Om, nom... Hmm. Hey! This is pretty good! I mean, of course it's good – it's Empery cuisine! Commander, open wide and I'll give you a dumpling alley oop. Say "aah"!

40405.name: Grain-Seizing Grani
40405.desc: Hah! This donut now belongs to Brünhilde! Alright, now for the finish line... C-Commander? Sorry, but there's no time for chit-chat... I'll be going now!

40501.name: Beacon of the Iron Blood
40501.desc: My sincerest apologies for the delay, Commander. Ah, excuse me... as the fleet leader of the Iron Blood, I'm expected to wear this outfit to various formal occasions. Just putting it on seems to make me inadvertently change the way I speak...

40501.name: Iron-Black Elysium
40501.desc: Welcome, what would you like to order? ...If you want, we can drop this charade. I'm not used to being a waiter anyway, so I prefer it this way. Hehe.

40502.name: Snow-Melting Summer
40502.desc: Summer... In the past, it was always just a hot and stifling season... But now...? Doesn't my outfit tell the whole story? Let's get going, there's bound to be a lot of people on the beach.

40502.name: Iron Blood Snowstorm
40502.desc: I bet Bismarck must've been thinking about how to invite me to the party, but ended up asking you to do it, Commander. Hehe... Let's get going soon. It's best not to keep her waiting.

40502.name: Seasonal Pine and the Frost Flower
40502.desc: They have a peculiar way of wishing a happy New Year in the Sakura Empire. In line with their traditions, I've put on this new outfit. I hope it doesn't... look strange on me. ...You like it? I see... That being the case, I'll keep wearing it for the time

40502.name: A Vase for the Frost Flower
40502.desc: It's all right, I just got here myself. I will say, it's strangely reassuring to know I'm not the only one nervous on this day.

40503.name: Mayhem Maid
40503.desc: *sigh* Do you really have to bother me during my break? ...It's a joke, no need to take it so seriously. I was looking for someone to kill some time with anyway.

40504.name: Tidying in the Moonlight
40504.desc: You, mop the floor. You, take care of the windows. Once that's done... Ah, Commander. Excuse us, we're in the middle of cleaning the area. If you have need of me, I must ask you to wait.

40601.name: Obsidian Elegance
40601.desc: I've been waiting for you, Comander. As per my sister's recommendation, I've put on this Sakura Empire kimono. It was very tricky to get into, I might add... That aside, how do I look? ...Good enough, I hope?

40601.name: Urbane Onyx
40601.desc: Ah, I've kept you waiting. I do apologize that it took so long to get changed into this outfit. Now, Commander, won't you come show me your chivalry and escort me down these stairs?

40601.name: Wave-Washed Paradise
40601.desc: I've been waiting forever for this season to arrive. It's a perfect time, the waves wait for nobody, so I'm off for now. I'll make sure to teach you how to surf later, so look forward to it.

40602.name: Time to Show Off?
40602.desc: Thank you all for waiting! Large mugs of Iron Blood beer, just as ord–– W-waaah?! Nnngh...! Phew, somehow managed to not spill anything... Wh-what's your deal?!

40602.name: Pure-Hearted Bad Girl
40602.desc: Still not here yet...? Geez, I'll give the Commander what-for for coming later than me... Huh? C-Commander? N-no, I happened to come an hour early, is all...

40701.name: Beachside Urd
40701.desc: So the Second Movement is a Lento of the summer and the sea? So be it... Since we will arrive at the Finale eventually, I suppose I can enjoy this moment of fleeting peace with you.

40703.name: Peter Strasser
40703.desc: Graf Zeppelin-class aircraft carrier – Peter Strasser.

40703.name: Chronos's Kalendae
40703.desc: Eugen, you said that this was is a ceremonial outfit from the Sakura Empire? Surprisingly, it does seem to suit me rather well. Oh, I'm supposed to offer my well-wishes for the New Year at this time, yes?

40703.name: A Moment Frozen in Pure White
40703.desc: You already know, don't you? Since I spent so much of my precious time changing into a dress for your sake... Heh, I'll be taking plenty of your time in return. Hehehe.

40801.name: U-81
40801.desc: Iron Blood Type VIIC submarine – U-81.

40801.name: Soft Serenade
40801.desc: *Ugh*... I figured this bulky dress would be hard to move in... Huh? I look pretty? Aha, ahaha... You're makin' me blush...

40801.name: Lantern-Lit Full Moon
40801.desc: Over here, Commander! I came because you said we were going to go moon-viewing together! I even brought tea and mooncakes.

40802.name: U-47
40802.desc: Iron Blood Type VIIB submarine – U-47.

40802.name: Rookie Rider
40802.desc: I haven't seen much of the world on land... Commander, want to explore it with me?

40802.name: Eigenen Raum
40802.desc: Sigh... I'd much rather be in a nice, quiet place like this over the din and clamor of the venue... Wouldn't you agree, Commander? I see. Well, come sit here then.

40802.name: Urban Maid
40802.desc: Coming through! Steer clear! Oh, it's you, Commander. Talk to you later – I've got coffee to deliver.

40802.name: Sanguine Moon Sojourn
40802.desc: An empty study with a cushy couch. The perfect place to relax. Whew... Go ahead and read a book if you want, Commander. If that'll be all then I'm gonna take a nap.

40802.name: Hook, Line, and Sinker
40802.desc: Nice. I've found a legendary luck-bringing carp, like... Oh. I almost had it, too... Sorry, Commander.

40803.name: U-557
40803.desc: Iron Blood Type VIIC submarine – U-557.

40804.name: U-556
40804.desc: Iron Blood Type VIIC submarine – U-556.

40804.name: Party Knight!
40804.desc: It's me, U-556, all prettied up! Eheheheh, we're gonna have lots of fun at this party, Commander! Come on, let's go!

40805.name: U-73
40805.desc: Iron Blood Type VIIB submarine – U-73.

40805.name: Science Rules!
40805.desc: It's time for science class with U-73! Now, Commander, let's try out an exhilarating and positively fascinating experiment!

40805.name: New Year's Chemistry
40805.desc: In today's chemistry lesson, we'll learn how to make a warming cup of tea and an optional concoction to enhance its flavor! Will you do the honor of taste-testing it, Commander?

40806.name: U-101
40806.desc: Iron Blood Type VIIC submarine – U-101.

40806.name: Ironbrass Trombonist
40806.desc: Commander, welcome to the school band! Why'd I join the band? The reason's simple - there's no Motorbike Club at school, haha! Just kidding~! Actually, I'm quite fond of music as well, heh.

40807.name: U-522
40807.desc: Iron Blood Type IXC submarine – U-522.

40808.name: U-110
40808.desc: Raaaawr. U-110 is a shaaaark. Fear meeee. Mess with me and I'll bite yooouuu.

40808.name: Kleiner Hai
40808.desc: Whenever I play games with Bulldog, I always end up losing. Frustratinggg. That's why... I'll study hard. One day, I'll winnnn.

40808.name: A Cute, Sharky Reverie
40808.desc: I have to wear beautiful clothes to a party, or so Bulldog said. So, I had everyone help me pick out beautiful clothes. Commander, I'm beautiful, right? Eh... cute?

40808.name: Garnished Supershark
40808.desc: The horned idol U-110 splashes onto the staaage. I'll sing all the baddies to obliviooon. I'm scaaary. Raaawr. Raaawr♪

40808.name: New Year, Small Shark
40808.desc: Commander, happy new yeeear. I'm no bunny, I'm a shaaark. Not a cute shark, but a crimson, scaaary shark. Raaawr.

40808.name: Springtime Shark
40808.desc: I'm gathering mushrooms, not garlic cloooves. The edible ones are gonna go in a hearty hot pot that'll warm me and my frieeends. Raaawr.

40809.name: U-96
40809.desc: Iron Blood Type VIIC submarine – U-96.

40809.name: Secret Gaming Session
40809.desc: Nice timing. I just finished an intense battle. The result...? Of course I won. What? Did you want to have a match against me?

40809.name: How Heavy Are Those Barbells?
40809.desc: Mmgh... Guh... Ahhh! These things are heavier than they look... Oh, there you are. You work out too, do ya? Feel free to join me if you've not just come to tease me.

40810.name: U-37
40810.desc: Iron Blood Type IXA submarine – U-37.

40810.name: New Year's Nightingale
40810.desc: Now then, please lend your ears to this song I shall offer you... Wait, Commander, are you spacing out again? Even though I went through all this trouble to learn this song from my friends in the Sakura fleet... Please pay attention, okay? I'm starting ov

40811.name: U-410
40811.desc: Iron Blood Type VIIC submarine – U-410.

40811.name: Spring Festival Scheme
40811.desc: Happy Lunar New Year. Have you cooked up a scheme for this year's festival? Hehehe~ I'm of course talking about giving out New Year's gifts and hanging up decorations. I've devised a master plan of my own.

40812.name: U-1206
40812.desc: Iron Blood Type VIIC submarine – U-1206

40812.name: Maid Just for You
40812.desc: Welcome! Oh, Hey, Commander! Heheh, so how do you like my maid getup? Looks pretty nice, if I do say so myself!

49901.name: Dark Red Grin
49901.desc: Such a delightful party with our wonderful friends in this peaceful harbor... It's wonderful, really... But, it's all so boring...

49901.name: Viridescent Lullaby
49901.desc: It's so nice getting away from the bustling party hall and being alone with you, Commander. I'm eager to see what we'll do now as your idea of a... "break"~

49902.name: Dark Raiments of Gagaku
49902.desc: I see, so this is a "kimono" from the Sakura Empire. Exquisitely crafted, comfortable to the touch, and elegantly designed... How to wear it? ...My child, what are you talking about?

49902.name: Zeremonie of the Cradle
49902.desc: Ahh, the dreamlike beauty of this variation... let us write down this movement so that it may continue forever, my sweet child.

49903.name: The Silkiest Brew
49903.desc: Ah! Changed already? Just wait a minute... No, you don't have to leave. I'm almost done.

49904.name: Black Strokes upon Blank Snow
49904.desc: I thought I would never have time to pursue the fine arts, and yet here I am now. Your thoughts, Commander? Eastern as this calligraphy may be, does it not suit the connotations of my name?

49905.name: Iron Blood's Dragon Maid
49905.desc: Hmph. They think being a maid is so difficult, do they? I could do this with my eyes clo– What?! H-how long have YOU been here?!

49905.name: Golden Dragon Among Auspicious Clouds
49905.desc: New decorations, new outfits, and countless preparations to make... Lunar New Year is quite the busy time of year. Go on, see to your duties. I'm well aware how essential you are to this holiday's smooth operation. Just don't keep me waiting all day. Heehee.

49906.name: The Conquered Unhulde
49906.desc: My hair is a mess... There we go. No, I don't need a hand. I am here to serve you in this fleeting dream of yours. Enjoy it while it lasts. Hehehe.

49907.name: The Gate Dragon's Advent
49907.desc: Woah, so this is the Dragon Empery's "Spring Festival" that I've heard so much about. But, why are they celebrating it in the middle of winter? And you, Commander – why are you helping with such a grandiose... Whuah?! What was that noise?!

50101.name: Setting Sun, Hearts as One
50101.desc: "Boundless is the beauty of evening's glow, but alas––" ...Oh, that doesn't have any special meaning, I've just been hanging around Hai Tien too much. (*whispers*) But, it's true... Our time together is far too short, just like the evening light...

50101.name: An Shan (Retrofit)
50101.desc: An Shan, retrofitting complete! With this new power, Commander, I'll protect both you and my sisters! But first... Umm, I need to double-check how these missiles work...!

50102.name: Fu Shun
50102.desc: An Shan-class destroyer No.2 - Fu Shun (102)

50102.name: The Unbreakable Baozi Heist
50102.desc: Heh-hey! Just hooked us another baozi~! We're in for one heckuva haul today! ...Eh? Huh, Commander?! Th-this is, uhh... yeah, we're just playing a normal game... totally...

50103.name: Chang Chun
50103.desc: An Shan-class destroyer No. 3 - Chang Chun (103)

50103.name: The Joy of Spring
50103.desc: Ta-da! My pajamas are finally finished! Now to snuggle up until I'm all warm! Eh~ Ehhh? But sis, I don't want to get out! Ack, did Tai Yuan purposely make this tail big and thick to make it easier for you?

50103.name: Fortune Arrives in Red
50103.desc: Commander, hurry up and plug your ears! Th-this isn't a joke! Um... Seriously, that big ol' doozy over there is about to blow!

50103.name: Chang Chun (Retrofit)
50103.desc: All done with my retrofit~ Now, time to test out my new toys... Err, I mean, time to test the firepower of my new armaments! Oh, watch your head, Commander! Wouldn't want one of the missiles to lock onto you.

50104.name: Tai Yuan
50104.desc: An Shan-class destroyer No. 4 - Tai Yuan (104)

50104.name: The Golden Dragon's Festivities
50104.desc: O-on behalf of the An Shan class, we wish a prosperous, happy, and healthy new year to Commander, and to everyone here at port... Umm... even though I made this outfit, I feel a bit embarrassed wearing it... Eh? It looks good on me? Um... th-thank you...

50201.name: Paragon of Celestial Grace
50201.desc: I am truly honored to be able to share this wondrous scenery with you on such a festive occasion, Commander. Umm... I'm not just saying that out of courtesy. We rarely get opportunities like this, so I'm somewhat flattered...

50201.name: Coronal Afterglow
50201.desc: Commander, thank you for waiting for me. Though I am unworthy of this honor, thank you so much...

50201.name: Yat Sen (Retrofit)
50201.desc: There's no need to worry, Commander. I will be fine now. Please allow me to serve you once more in this new form.

50202.name: Ning Hai
50202.desc: Ning Hai-class Light Cruiser, Ning Hai

50202.name: Summer Hunger
50202.desc: Summer’s all about the beach! And the beach is all about good food! Commander, let’s find something delicious to eat!

50202.name: Moon Palace Rabbit
50202.desc: Happy Mid-Autumn Festival! I heard that if you pray to the moon today, you’ll become as pretty as the Goddess of the Moon! ...Eh? You’re gonna pray too?

50202.name: Dragon Sisters! -N
50202.desc: We haven't had to worry as much about things like food since we joined the fleet, but that doesn't mean we can just throw money around...! Anyway, I'm the older of the "Dragon Sisters," Ning Hai! Great to be here!

50202.name: Springtime Sojourn
50202.desc: Commander, what are you spacing out for? Over here! They say that you'll have good fortune if you give this thing a shake!

50202.name: Gorgeous Violet
50202.desc: Yat Sen said this look would be best for a party, but, is it really okay? I'm not used to having my hair down like this...

50202.name: Da Bao's Friend!
50202.desc: Good boy. Chew thoroughly before you swallow. I never thought I'd help with a charity event for nature, but Da Bao's made a lot of new friends because of it. Keep up the good work, Commander and Ping!

50202.name: Ning Hai (Retrofit)
50202.desc: Yes! … this feels good. Thank you, Commander. In order to live up to your expectations, from now on, I will be more serious around you, Commander. Hey, don't run!

50203.name: Ping Hai
50203.desc: Ning Hai-class Light Cruser, Ping Hai

50203.name: Summer Vacation
50203.desc: Compared to pork buns, shaved ice is tastier. Compared to shaved ice, fireworks are prettier. Compared to fireworks, what I care for the most is...

50203.name: Osmanthus Moon Rabbit
50203.desc: Happy Mid-Autumn Festival, Commander! Mooncakes, pomegranates, and osmanthus cakes... what a wonderful holiday!

50203.name: Dragon Sisters! -P
50203.desc: Big sister says that even though we have some money now, we still have to save as much as we can. Um... Anyway, I'm the younger "Dragon Sister," Ping Hai. Erm... I'm kind of hungry. Do you maybe have something to eat?

50203.name: Great Gourmet Expedition
50203.desc: The Sakura Empire has lots of delicious food that I've never tried before! Yeah! It's a great place!

50203.name: Delicious Crimson
50203.desc: There's always a lot of delicious food at these parties! But, my sister said I'm not allowed to have any cake until everyone's gotten their slice... Baobao, let's be on our best behavior!

50203.name: Baobao's Buddy!
50203.desc: Cheese! That came out looking good! Hehehe~ I'm really glad to be a part of this charity event for nature, along with you and my sister! Baobao is really glad too!

50203.name: Ping Hai (Retrofit)
50203.desc: Hi~ya! Hmm... this feels... nothing special. Baobao looks happy though... Never mind, Commander, Ping Hai is hungry!

50204.name: Ying Swei
50204.desc: Chao Ho-class protected cruiser – Ying Swei.

50204.name: Snowy Pine's Warmth
50204.desc: Happy New Year, Commander. I've come to deliver you blessings for this coming year... Next, you're going to ask for a red envelope, right? Hehe, just teasing~

50204.name: Frolicking Flowers, Verse I
50204.desc: Commander, Happy New Year! Chao Ho and I are preparing for this year's Spring Festival, and as you can see... we're in the middle of a little "intermission." Hehe, don't worry, there's nothing you need to help out with. Just take a seat over there and enjoy the show~

50205.name: Chao Ho
50205.desc: Chao Ho-class protected cruiser – Chao Ho.

50205.name: Plum Blossom's Illumination
50205.desc: Happy New Year, Commander! This red envelope is my gift to you... after all, that's my responsibility as a big sister! Anyway, hurry up and take it!

50205.name: Frolicking Flowers, Verse II
50205.desc: Happy... New Year... Commander... Gah, this isn't the time for pleasantries! And you, help me catch the dumb fluffball that ran off with our ornaments! Jeez, why is this happening when I'm in the middle of getting ready for the Spring Festival?!

50207.name: Hai Tien
50207.desc: Hai Tien-class protected cruiser – Hai Tien.

50207.name: Verse-Weaver at the Water's Edge
50207.desc: What a serendipitous meeting this is, Commander. I was simply searching for a place where I could leisurely enjoy my poetry manuscript. Since fate has brought both of us here, why don't we accompany each other for a while?

50208.name: Hai Chi
50208.desc: Hai Tien-class protected cruiser – Hai Chi.

50208.name: A Dance Among the Lotuses
50208.desc: Look, Commander! I've become a goddess from the Dragon Empery's folklore! Hehehe! Let me perform for you a song and dance number I just learned!

50601.name: Vestibule of Wonders
50601.desc: You're here, Commander, just as promised. How do you like the atmosphere in here? Hehe, take a seat and enjoy the tea slowly. After all, we have plenty of time~

50601.name: Cerulean Ripples
50601.desc: Oh my, if it isn't the Commander... Have you also come to escape the heat? What a serendipitous meeting... Or, did you perhaps have some other goal in mind? Heehee...

50602.name: The Festive Undead
50602.desc: I am Hwah Jah, now in zombie form. It is an honor to see you– hmm? What's wrong, Commander? Everyone else is getting dressed up for the occasion, so I figured I'd get in on the action too... Is there something wrong with that?

51901.name: Tender White Jade
51901.desc: I see, so this is how you're supposed to knead dough... Hmm? Commander? As you can see, I'm currently trying to make baozi. Would you like to help out?

59901.name: Union Between Sea and Sky
59901.desc: Pheeew! I just love blue skies and a fair ocean breeze. Since you're already here, Commander, set aside all the boring paperwork and business stuff, and come enjoy the waves!

60102.name: Refreshing Sundress
60102.desc: Lady Veneto advised me to enjoy my time off by changing into something befitting the occasion... Um, Commander, I d-don't look strange, do I?

60103.name: Fair Lady's Invitation
60103.desc: "To refuse a fair signorina's invitation would be most uncouth"... Hehe~ Now, Commander, would you like to partake in some refreshments? Rest assured, they're all non-alcoholic♪

60104.name: Lonesome Beachfarer
60104.desc: It's way too crowded on the beach... I'd much rather be– Oh, Commander? Are you not good with crowded places either...?

60105.name: Beachbound Southwestern Wind!
60105.desc: Libeccio's heading towards the sea! Commander, let's go to where all the excitement is!

60106.name: To a Smashing Voyage!
60106.desc: I know this one! It's that Sakura Empire watermelon-smashing game! Just put the melon over there, Commander! ...Relax, it'll be fine! Have some faith in my navigator's intuition! Ready? Then let's go!

60107.name: Quaver Daydream
60107.desc: *yawn*... Nothing's impossible when you've got Captain Pompey... Hmm? Commander? Wait, I fell asleep? Seems I did... Drat, I forgot what I even came here for...

60108.name: Vivacious Vivace
60108.desc: Found you, Commander! How would you grade this outfit of mine? ...No, no, I wasn't asking if it looked cute or pretty, I wanted to know if I was wearing it right in the first place! You know what though, I think I'll take those compliments~

60109.name: Backstage Blunders
60109.desc: Eek! Wh-why are you guys tugging at my stockings... P-please stop that... C-Commander, please... Hurry and come help me! Waah...

60201.name: Duca degli Abruzzi
60201.desc: Duca degli Abruzzi-class light cruiser – Luigi di Savoia Duca degli Abruzzi.

60201.name: Lustrous Onyx Sirenetta
60201.desc: Good evening, Commander. Here to unwind after a day's work, I take it? Even dignitaries desire a bit of luxury sometimes. Hahaha.

60202.name: Giuseppe Garibaldi
60202.desc: Duca degli Abruzzi-class light cruiser – Giuseppe Garibaldi.

60202.name: Noble Ivory Plumes
60202.desc: I am the evil swan Odile! Where oh where is my prince? ...Oh, it's you, Commander. My lines aside, pretty good performance, right?

60301.name: Summer's Hotness?
60301.desc: The summer's scorching heat is alleviated by the ocean~ Commander, why don't you set aside your worries and... cut loose a bit~?

60302.name: Poolside Coincidence
60302.desc: Phew... It's a perfect day for swimming. Oh my, Commander, did you come to swim too? Or... perhaps you had something else in mind? Ehehe~♪

60303.name: Seaside Coincidence
60303.desc: Zara, how dastardly of you to spike the ball at such a time– Eek?! Commander?! Why are you in a place like that?

60304.name: Rooftop Lunch Break
60304.desc: Oh my, are you done with your errands already? Surely, you didn't skip work just to eat lunch with... Ah, sorry for doubting you. Alright, let's go. Trento is waiting for us.

60304.name: Amore Termico
60304.desc: Whew... I'm getting dizzy... I'll rest in the breeze for a moment. You okay, Commander? Step out if it's too hot. See, someone will worry about you...

60305.name: A Flutter in the Moment
60305.desc: I've never had a knack for dancing or exercise unlike Zara and her sisters... but if asked, I will dance as best as I can! Please keep your eyes on me, Commander!

60305.name: Tempting Treasure
60305.desc: So... The premise is that you and I were shipwrecked and ended up on a desert island... Is that right, Commander? I see... But if we weren't actually shipwrecked... what is this treasure, then?

60501.name: The Flower of La Spezia
60501.desc: Nngh, haah... It's awfully sunny today... How long was I asleep, Commander? Oh, it's already lunchtime? In that case, I'll get started on some food. Would you like something as well?

60502.name: The Glory of Naples
60502.desc: A visit to the beach with me? Then you must try your hardest to stand out. Otherwise the eyes of the world will be on me alone.

60502.name: Calabria Aurea
60502.desc: Welcome to Littorio's personal suite. Are you here to issue me a challenge of who can romance the most girls? Hahahah, I'm joking of course! There'd be no fun in a game I would win every single time.

60502.name: Lounging Emerald
60502.desc: Hello there. You'll have to forgive the loungewear; I have scarcely any reason to wear extravagant clothes in my private space away from the public eye.

60503.name: White Heron of Darkest Night
60503.desc: You seem to have known that I would be here. Then stay and spend the night with me. Just the two of us.

60505.name: Conte di Cavour
60505.desc: Conte di Cavour-class battleship – Conte di Cavour.

60505.name: Fierce Beachside Battle
60505.desc: Commander, take this. Good, for the time being, you are a now a disciple under my command. It is time for us to mete out punishment to the unruly.

60506.name: Giulio Cesare
60506.desc: Conte di Cavour-class battleship – Giulio Cesare.

60506.name: Fitness Master
60506.desc: Both exercise and war are at their core about willpower! Now, get ready, Commander! We're not finished until you're dripping with sweat!

60506.name: High Tide Under the Sunlight
60506.desc: Tired already? For goodness' sake, I thought you'd be more reliable than this. Don't go burning all your energy at once, we still have a whole day of recreation ahead of us.

60701.name: Sardegnian Shallows and Sunshine
60701.desc: Good day, my Commander. We have the day off to enjoy the sea breeze and the ocean waves~ Hehe, would you like to help yourself to some fruit?

60701.name: A Sip of Sardegnian Elegance
60701.desc: Oh, my Commander? I didn't expect to meet you here! Fortune smiles upon me today. Hehe~ If you have a minute to spare, would you care to join me for a cup of tea?

60702.name: Languid Librarian
60702.desc: Seems school uniforms are all the hype. Veneto picked this one out for me. What are you dressed as, Commander? A teacher? A classmate?

60801.name: Shady Seaside
60801.desc: Hehe, hehehehe... We have this little c-corner of the beach all to ourselves... Now, what should we do first... Hehehehe...

60802.name: Riverside Pirouette
60802.desc: Here to watch me rehearse just like these deer, Commander? Isn't it wonderful being surrounded by the beauty of nature? For a performance based on a fable such as this one, ambiance is key. Ehehe~♪

69901.name: The Queen of Hearts
69901.desc: Me? Serve as your maid? Oho! That's more like it, Commander! How magnificent and ambitious of you! ...Only temporarily? And you're content with that?

70102.name: Bad Bunny Behind Bars
70102.desc: Comrade Commander, are you here to see my room? Hm? That Шутки isn't funny? Then how about... did my room come to see you, comrade Commander?

70102.name: Bunny Remodeling Plan?
70102.desc: Hmm... If I tweak Królik around a bit like this... But, it'll probably be a problem if I don't finish this in one go... Guess I'll think about it while I eat. Mhm.

70102.name: Shadowy Syndicate Showdown
70102.desc: Our shift starts now. Królik, Pirožkí, Manjuus – form up! Let us realize our Manjuu comrades' dreams!

70102.name: Tea Party with Królik
70102.desc: *burp*... Now I think I get the appeal of tea. Why is the cup so small, though? Do you have a bigger one on hand, Comrade Commander?

70102.name: Bunny in the Banya
70102.desc: Uughh... Ooohh... Królik is melting... *gasp*! I'm getting lightheaded... Comrade Commander, fetch me some ice...

70103.name: Thunderous Jailor
70103.desc: You've violated the Minsk Protocol, comrade! Therefore, the sentence appropriate for you is imprisonment! Until when? Obviously, until your jailor is satisfied~♪

70104.name: The Bound Cruiser
70104.desc: ...*Sigh*, I never thought I'd get captured by these little guys... Dear comrade, does Tashkent really have to play along with this?

70104.name: The Blue Snoozer
70104.desc: Urrk... Who dares disturb Tashkent's slumber? ...Oh, it's you, dear comrade? Um, in that case... I can always get more rest later. Is something the matter?

70105.name: Tashkent μ
70105.desc: How do you like my outfit, dear comrade? ...Is that so? After all of Tashkent's work to become an idol, that's how you react? Hmph. Just you wait. My next concert will rock your socks off.

70106.name: No Snow No Life
70106.desc: It sucks not being able to play in the snow... Oh well! I'll play some games instead! Commander, let's play something fun together!

70107.name: A Daytime Delight is in a Book
70107.desc: Wh-who gave you the right to just barge in? ...I did? Huh. Well, seeing as you're here, I guess we could read a book together. Mm, that's all.

70108.name: Morning's Beckoning
70108.desc: Comrade! The morning is already here! Look how high the sun is in the sky!! C'mon, a wonderful day is calling to us~!!

70109.name: The Machinery of Life
70109.desc: Yes, these data and results are quite interesting... Though they mean nothing to me! I am a genius mechanic, not an analyst! Ahh-ha-ha-haah!

70110.name: Backstreet Silver Sonata
70110.desc: Seeing you here puts me at ease. I know this stakeout will go smoothly as long as you're here. Mhm, all is fine.

70201.name: Shackled Saule
70201.desc: "I am Avrora, the princess bound within this tower by a cruel fate... My beloved, please come for me soon..."

70201.name: Not Cut Out For This?
70201.desc: "Muahaha... Now, these streets belong to me..." Sorry, I bit my tongue... Hmm, getting into this role is quite difficult for me after all.

70202.name: Caged Minx
70202.desc: What kinda exercise is this?! Nobody said I'd become a dang showpiece! Come on, get this thing off me, NOW!

70202.name: Sweet Cherry Memories
70202.desc: Mmmh~ I sure could get used to this life~ Oh, Commander, thanks for being my gofer~♪ Ah, you can leave the cherries right over here!

70202.name: Chic and Cheeky
70202.desc: Aaand send DM to Rossiya... Finally you showed up, Commander! So, where are you taking me, hmm?

70202.name: Mercurial Chocolate Love
70202.desc: Happy Valentine's Day~♪ Did you come here to enjoy my chocolate? Then, try guessing where I hid my chocolate – if you get it right, I'll give it to you~♪ Is it here... or maybe over here? Ahahaha~♡

70202.name: Pamiat' Merkuria (Retrofit)
70202.desc: My retrofitting is done! Look forward to seeing how both my cuteness and combat potential have been upgraded!

70203.name: The Captive Cavalier
70203.desc: Commander, what's going on? Did I... do something wrong...? This was all just... meant to be an exercise, right?

70203.name: White Cavalier's Respite
70203.desc: Phew... Oh my, Commander, I'm sorry I didn't welcome you at the door. You don't have to be so tense - I already know not to try doing anything weird with you. Hehe~

70203.name: Indigo & Lantern-Lit Summer Night
70203.desc: You've been looking for me? Heehee, sorry if I made you worry, I just had to feel the night breeze in my hair for a bit. Why don't you stay and enjoy it with me?

70204.name: Blend R
70204.desc: Comrade Commander, you've come at a good time. I've recently taken a liking to this blend of coffee. Want some as well? No need to be shy.

70204.name: Drifting Justice
70204.desc: Halt! You have nowhere left to run!! ...Well done, Comrade Commander, what a thrilling chase we had on our hands! What, you think I'm well-suited for this job? You tease too much, bahaha!

70204.name: High Jump Star
70204.desc: ...Hmph! Just short of a new personal best, huh? But make no mistake, Comrade Commander. Keep watching me and your patience WILL be rewarded with a breathtaking record!

70205.name: Maestro of Sterling Strings
70205.desc: ...Thus marks the end of this tune. The Dragon Empery has graciously allowed me to perform in their Spring Festival celebration. Are you here to listen, Commander? In that case... How did you like the song? Heehee.

70206.name: Sceneries of Pure Snow
70206.desc: ...Achoo! Uhh, good morning... Snow? Yeah, it is snowing today... Woah, it's really coming down hard... Ahaha~

70207.name: Devoted as the Warm Snow
70207.desc: Comrade Commander, is the bath to your liking? I'm glad. Heehee, it's a good thing I trusted that "Top 10 Dates for Snowy Days" article and chose this secluded hot spring.

70301.name: Nostalgic Pilsner
70301.desc: What, you've never seen the inside of a shipgirl's room? It's not like you're here on official business, so stop standing around already. Find a place to sit and relax.

70301.name: As You Say, Ma'am!
70301.desc: You've reached the Bureau of Investigation... Oh boy, another case. Commander, finish up your paperwork ASAP. We've got witnesses to interview.

70302.name: Lone Wolf Amid the Steam
70302.desc: This steamy hot spring... is a rather novel experience. I left a spot for you, so come sit down already – Wait, why haven't you taken your clothes off yet?

70501.name: Imposing Warden
70501.desc: You have my thanks for this exercise, comrade! I shall gladly carry out the important duty of judge, jury, and rehabilitator!

70501.name: Keeper of the Firewater
70501.desc: ...Bwahaah! I've had all kinds of liquor, but nothing beats the stuff back home! Comrade, let's have a toast to the coming off-duty days!

70504.name: Relaxation Stratagem
70504.desc: To pass the time by proactively reading, or by passively enjoying the company of others... Ah, good morning, Comrade, I've been expecting you. Hahaha!

70505.name: The Lackadaisical Lookout
70505.desc: "Situation normal in all sectors of the facility..." Oh, it is you. I was just giving Minsk the daily report. Do you have something?

70506.name: Grandiose Getaway
70506.desc: Your choice treasure now belongs to master thief Arkhangelsk! Think you can arrest me? Then stop gawking and come get me!

70507.name: More than a Little Drunk
70507.desc: Phew... This is... Comrade Commander? Fancy meeting you at this time of night. Me? Heh, heheheheh... You wouldn't believe me if I said I got too drunk and went in first, would you?

70701.name: An Irresistible AR Adventure
70701.desc: Volga here. I'm currently tracking an important witness. *gurgle* ...Is my stomach rumbling because this AR game requires so much stamina? Ugh, lost track of the witness just now...

71801.name: Begin the Rush!
71801.desc: Listen up, assholes! We have you surrounded! I'm Kronshtadt, squad leader of the Northern Parliament Special Forces! You have only one option: come out with your hands in the air and surrender!

79901.name: Seaside Sunset
79901.desc: Oh? What made you come over here instead of heading down to the beach? Surely you didn't ditch your friends on a hard-earned day off just to see me? But, I don't mind. It's called a day off because you get to decide how to spend your time.

80102.name: Fleur Blanche
80102.desc: It's good to be able to stop and smell the roses every now and then. Um, Commander, would you be able to accompany me a bit longer?

80102.name: École de Chevalier
80102.desc: Even though I'm an Iris Libre squire, I'm currently working hard to have a rich student life. Um... maybe this is a bit too laid back?

80102.name: Feast of Champagne
80102.desc: Good evening, Commander. I am currently enjoying the party in the company of my friends, as my duties as a squire entail. Um... I've had a bit too much to drink? R-really...?

80102.name: Fleur de Mariée
80102.desc: At long last, this wonderful day is here. It feels like I'm dreaming... I'm so happy, I just... Forgive me, I promised myself I wouldn't cry... I, Forbin the squire, shall remain by your side for the rest of my life!

80102.name: Forbin (Retrofit)
80102.desc: My hard work has finally paid off! Commander, thank you for your guidance all this time! I'll return the favor by bringing you even more honors in battle!

80103.name: Summery Temeraire!
80103.desc: Commander, I've finished changing into my swimsuit! Heheh~ let's head down to the beach and enjoy ourselves as much as we can!

80103.name: Dreamy Dolce
80103.desc: How do I look? These pajamas are super cute, aren't they? Ehehe, I really like this one! It even matches with Opiniâtre's!

80104.name: Beachside Magician
80104.desc: It is said that the summertime sea holds an extraordinary enchantment over people... but the only supernatural thing I'm feeling is this accursed heat... Am I missing something?

80107.name: Le Terrible
80107.desc: Le Fantasque-class large destroyer - Le Terrible.

80107.name: Silence, Slumber, and Solace
80107.desc: Zzz... Commander...? Sorry... for showing you this unsightly side of mine... I'm just, not a morning person... Zzzzz...

80107.name: Sunlight, Seaspray, and Sanctity
80107.desc: How goes your day, Commander? Hehe, are you looking for my clever sister, Le Malin? If so, you would do well to search somewhere less... popular~♪

80108.name: The Noble Knight's Last Stand
80108.desc: H-h-halt, intruder! Thou art intruding in the domain of an Iris Libre Templar Knight, a crime punishable by... Eek! I'm begging you, spare my life! ...It's you, Lord Commander?!

80108.name: Sugary Sabbatical
80108.desc: Enjoying sweet pastries in a lovely dress – heehee, such bliss! ...I care not how unbecoming this is of a knight! I saved these desserts for my holiday! Let me enjoy myself, would you!

80201.name: Côte d'Azur
80201.desc: Commander, does my swimsuit pique your fancy? I'm actually quite proud of my fashion sense. *Giggle* Now, let's enjoy midsummer together~

80201.name: Maid Fantastique
80201.desc: I heard of this romantic concept of maid outfits, and thought I'd try one on to see how it feels~ What are your thoughts, Commander?

80201.name: Gilded Dance
80201.desc: Modest though it may be, isn't this a lovely little garden? Come, Commander! Let us dance surrounded by Mother Nature~

80201.name: Émile Bertin (Retrofit)
80201.desc: Émile Bertin, retrofit complete! I feel like a completely new person! To show my gratitude, Commander, I'll perform a brand new dance for you!

80202.name: Saintess of the Sea
80202.desc: "O chosen hero, I bestow this sword upon you so that you may clear any obstacles in your path..." Commander, how did that sound?

80501.name: Fleuron of the Waves
80501.desc: This swimsuit... Yes, the one Émile picked out for me, seems a bit skimpy... I didn't think she'd be the type to trick me into wearing something like this, but... Commander, where are you looking?

80501.name: Evergreen Prophecy
80501.desc: Commander, I wish you a Happy New Year. May you avail yourself of the period of repose that follows the culmination of the year's duties. I pray that you and everyone else may receive the blessing of the Heavens.

80701.name: Summer Lifeguard
80701.desc: Are you perhaps feeling unwell, Commander? Oh, I see, you're just looking for a shaded place to rest? Acknowledged. In that case, you may sit here if you'd like.

80801.name: Shopping Time!
80801.desc: Hmm? Commander, are you shopping as well? If so, why don't you come along and take a look around? ... Huh? Of course you can't climb on. That'd be illegal.

80801.name: Loisirs Balnéaires
80801.desc: Mmmh~ Bonjour, Commander~ Nothing feels better than the waves lapping at your skin~ Oh, Commander, why don't you come lie down and experience it for yourself?

89901.name: Holy Knight's Resplendence
89901.desc: With all due respect, Commander, this finery and this throne are not fit for one such as myself. Despite the hallowed name I have inherited, I am nothing more than a warrior. —However, if such an arrangement pleases you, then I shall hold my objections.

89901.name: Alluring Administrator
89901.desc: Commander, regarding your next appointment... Ah, hard work is one of the highest virtues of the Iris's holy knights. On weekdays or vacations, in knights' armor or the Dragon Empery's attire, there can be no pause to my prayer, my training, or my duties as the administrator of your will.

89902.name: Lapis Lazuli's First Dream
89902.desc: It is not against the teachings to halt one's pursuit of destiny and to surrender to the warm draft of festivities. It is mankind's prerogative to seek out auspicious portents.

89903.name: Marine Muse
89903.desc: "I devote this paean to thee, Champion of seas blue and free." There, the song is completed. But we've come all this way... Shall we continue our adventure through these undersea ruins, Champion?

90101.name: Été Brillant
90101.desc: It's summer~! Summer is here, Commander! Let's head down to the beach to play! I'll show you why I'm feared in water gun fights!

90101.name: Écolière Heureuse
90101.desc: Hey! Over here! Hehe. I didn't expect to run into you at school, Commander. What are you doing here?

90101.name: Splendorous Debut
90101.desc: Commander, thanks for coming to pick me up! I don't often get the chance to wear formal clothes, though it is a little hard to move around... Oh, but I can deal with it!

90101.name: Le Mars (Retrofit)
90101.desc: Retro~ fit~ com~ plete! The new and improved Le Mars is at your service~!

90102.name: Overthinking Summer
90102.desc: Commander, you're not going to get into the water? ...Ah, I'm fine right here. To tell you the truth, I once got washed away by the waves, and then got laughed at by Vauquelin... so I'm perfectly fine right here.

90103.name: Innocent Summer Knight
90103.desc: Commandeeer! What are you doing? It's our day off! Turn the work part of your brain off and just have fun! C'mon, let's enjoy ourselves on the beach!

90103.name: One-Girl Orchestra
90103.desc: Yes, the strings... I can hear the celebratory melody... Now, follow my lead and we'll take this song to greater– Oh, Commander? What's all this, you ask? Uhh... You know... Ahahaha...

90103.name: Otherworldly Adventure
90103.desc: *crash*! Found another coin! Check it out, Commander! I got all these from smashing pots! ...Breaking the law? Heheh! The one law among thieves is that there are no laws♪

90111.name: Sleepy Sunday
90111.desc: Morning, Commander~ Mm, the Sabbath is the day of rest, so I shall not budge from my sacred charge even if you were to call Triomphant over. I solemnly swear to do absolutely nothing today.

90111.name: Mercredi at the Secret Base
90111.desc: I must commend you for being able to find my secret base, Commander... but unfortunately for you, I refuse to return to the office today. Just... *yawn*...let me spend the whole day sleeping here...

90111.name: Listless Lapin
90111.desc: Zzz... zzz... Huh? Commander? I was in the middle of a nap... Oh, this outfit? It's cool, comfy, and cute. If you don't need anything from me, I'm going back to sleep...

90112.name: Le Malin μ
90112.desc: I am the Iris's shining sword, Le Malin. As the shimmering idol who chases the waves, may your souls be healed by my songs of prayer.

90113.name: Little Red Riding Hood's Worries
90113.desc: What a farce, making a proud Templar Knight portray a helpless little girl... Why am I lying here, you ask? Hmph. Because Le Malin asserted this is the best way to get in touch with my "vulnerable side"...

90113.name: Temp in Low Temperatures
90113.desc: Hmm... Traveling by foot from here would be quickest. Ah... It's snowing. Hmph! A little snow and wind can scarcely faze a noble Templar Knight! I'll be back shortly!

90201.name: La Galissonnière
90201.desc: La Galissonnière-class light cruiser – La Galissonnière.

90201.name: Pristine Piscene
90201.desc: Summertime means pool time! Oh, hey, Commander. What are you waiting for? Come over and let's have fun!

90201.name: Lush Spring Dreams
90201.desc: Happy New Year, again! So, you wanna try sharing this "cross-cupped wine?" What, it's not a drinking game? Welp, I guess I've still got a whole ton to learn about the Dragon Empery's customs~

90201.name: Black Cat of All Hallows' Eve
90201.desc: If you ignore me, I'll use my black cat magic to turn you into a pumpkin! Is that Halloweeny enough? Ahahaha! I'm just messing! C'mon, let's go do somethin' fun tonight, Commander!

90301.name: Rainbow Rendezvous
90301.desc: Yo, Commander, did I keep you waiting? Sorry 'bout that. You know how it goes, sometimes it's really hard for a girl to pick out the right thing to wear. Anyway, let's get going~♪

90302.name: White Sand Paradise
90302.desc: Oh my, hehe... Are you enjoying the warmth of the sunlight here? I'm glad that you're finding some time to relax here, but wouldn't you rather come play with everyone else?

90302.name: Red Queen's Decree
90302.desc: Oh my, it seems that the one who ended up coming wasn't little Alice, but you instead... Do you plan to defy me as well, Commander? If so, I'll have to put you on trial for your sins... How was my acting just now? Hehe~

90401.name: Summer Sucré
90401.desc: I've been waiting so long for summer... and it's so worth it - the sun, the sand, the waves, and everyone's laughter. Commander, why don't we take this opportunity to enjoy some crullers together?

90401.name: Afternoon Venus
90401.desc: Don't you simply adore the atmosphere in this place? It's one of my favorites. The desserts here are to die for. Would you like a taste?

90501.name: Uninhibited Bloodstone
90501.desc: The guest of honor shouldn't be wandering around looking for girls drinking alone... Hmph, might as well have a drink while you're here anyway.

90501.name: Private Après Midi
90501.desc: You damn scalawag... You don't just sneak into someone's hideaway without consequences, ya know. Though, I found this place by pure chance too. Don't go tellin' anyone else about it!

90501.name: First Snow Upon the Cutlass's Edge
90501.desc: Bonne année... Or rather, I should say "Happy New Year" here, yes? A year of peace and prosperity passes, and we are here to welcome another... and I must thank you for making that possible.

90503.name: Gascogne μ
90503.desc: Gascogne module change process complete. New directive: sing for the world. Master's order is my will.

90701.name: Ensorcelled Snow White
90701.desc: Were you planning on freeing me from this spell? Then I suppose you're prepared to lock lips with me. Even though I'm already awake, um... that's just part of the ritual.

90701.name: Sublime Elysium
90701.desc: Do you feel refreshed? Even without a holy ritual, the Iris would be happy to know that I've managed to soothe you with this bath. Was it not enough? Then... Shall we go back in?

99901.name: Tropical Environs Acclimation Service Equipment
99901.desc: Gascogne uniform change complete. Directive assigned: have fun on the beach with Master. Requesting detailed instructions for how to "have fun on the beach."

960001.name: Treats from the Deep
960001.desc: Tonight's dessert is not a cake or a pastry... What are you looking around for? YOU'RE my dessert! Heheh, scared you, didn't I?

970101.name: Hunter META
970101.desc: Greetings, Commander. I'm Hunter. I hunt, as you might've surmised. Is this place... my new base?

970102.name: Fortune META
970102.desc: Well met, Commander. My name is Fortune. Please don't worry about these ch-chains... They're there to... keep my power in check.

970201.name: Helena META
970201.desc: Were you looking for me? I am willing to lend you my power – provided that you promise not to hide anything from me.

970202.name: Memphis META
970202.desc: I'm Memphis. You may not know me, but I know you and I know you well. Don't you worry, I'm not a threat – you can trust me. Today I assume the role of your right hand and bodyguard.

970203.name: Sheffield META
970203.desc: So you're the Commander... in other words, my Master. Alright, got it. The name's Sheffield, and the game's pointing my gun at vermin – Ah, please disregard that little gesture I made just now.

970204.name: La Galissonnière META
970204.desc: I'm La Galissonnière, the shipgirl from hell! I've come for your soul! ...Wow, didn't even flinch. Guess it's true that you don't fear death. Heheh, let's see if I can get a more interesting response out of you next time~♪

970301.name: Trento META
970301.desc: I am heavy cruiser Trento, and I will be your assistant. The best thing I could ask for is that my support helps you achieve your goals.

970401.name: Gneisenau META
970401.desc: You're... the Commander, right? In other words, the one with the authority to control me. Though I have no interest in you as an individual, I will still obey your orders... At least for the time being.

970402.name: Scharnhorst META
970402.desc: I'm Iron Blood battlecruiser Scharnhorst. I am keen to join forces with a Commander as talented as you. Don't let my expectations of you be misplaced.

970403.name: Repulse META
970403.desc: I'm Repulse, Renown-class battlecruiser. I've been through a lot... but that's in the past. Now, I'm a part of this port. Whenever you're in a pinch, come see me.

970404.name: Renown META
970404.desc: Salutations to you, Commander. I am battlecruiser Renown. I hope that this battle-worn blade can become your power.

970501.name: Fusou META
970501.desc: I am battleship Fusou. I have come to bring peace to this world's tormented souls. Commander, do you seek blessings... or redemption?

970502.name: Yamashiro META
970502.desc: Are you this fleet's Commander, Milord? I see. You have great potential, but your skills need some refinement. I wonder what's the best way to train you... You'll see soon enough – stay alert until then!

970503.name: Arizona META
970503.desc: I am Arizona... This may be improper of me, but is it really alright for me to stay here? ...Very well, Commander. If that is what you've decided...

970504.name: Queen Elizabeth META
970504.desc: So you are the Commander? Very well. From this point forth, you will use your courage and intellect for our purposes! ...We don't have all day, now. You are our servant, so this won't go anywhere until you swear your fealty.

970601.name: Hiyou META
970601.desc: Ahahahaha! The fact that you've chosen me means you clearly have a discerning eye. So, what now? Where's the enemy you need me to sink?

970602.name: Junyou META
970602.desc: I'm... Junyou. Please give me your orders... Commander.

970701.name: Hiryuu META
970701.desc: I'm getting all fired up! The name's Hiryuu, Hiryuu from the 2nd CarDiv. As a member of this fleet, I'll obey your orders. I do hope that you are qualified to lead us.

970702.name: Ark Royal META
970702.desc: Aircraft carrier Ark Royal, at your service. I hereby vow to lend you my strength for as long as you harbour honourable ambitions!

970703.name: Souryuu META
970703.desc: I am Souryuu of the Sakura Empire's 2nd CarDiv. Let's skip the formalities and get to work right away.

1010001.name: Neptune
1010001.desc: Heya! My name's Neptune! Nice to meet you!

1010002.name: Noire
1010002.desc: Are you the commander? Hmm... Very well. I'm Noire. The CPU of Lastation. You can put your mind at ease now that I'm here.

1010003.name: Blanc
1010003.desc: I'm Blanc. Nice to meet you. Maybe you could introduce some intriguing books from this world to me...

1010004.name: Vert
1010004.desc: My name is Vert, I am the CPU of Leanbox. I'm very good at first-person shooters, so please let me handle all combat-related matters!

1010005.name: Purple Heart
1010005.desc: I am Purple Heart, the CPU of Planeptune. And you must be the commander. I will follow your orders from now.

1010005.name: Goddesses' Promise
1010005.desc: Oh, Commander? Won't you join me in a short conversation? I'll tell you things about Planeptune. Oh, and I'm eagerly awaiting the day you come to Planeptune for a visit.

1010006.name: Black Heart
1010006.desc: I'm the CPU of Lastation, Black Heart. I've rushed here all the way from Gamindustri to lend you my aid. Be grateful.

1010006.name: Goddesses' Smile
1010006.desc: It's good to take it easy and celebrate once in a while, but especially in moments like these, you can't afford to let your guard down. Commander, why don't we spar for a bit? Don't even think about holding back - come at me!

1010007.name: White Heart
1010007.desc: I'm White Heart, the guardian CPU of Lowee. Pleased to meet you. I'm gonna give you a taste of a CPU's power!

1010007.name: Goddesses' Humility
1010007.desc: B-bastard! Where are you looking? I bet you're thinking I look like a kid! Eh....? They're just right? If Commander says something like that... I don't know how to react...

1010008.name: Green Heart
1010008.desc: I am the CPU of Leanbox, Green Heart. No matter who the enemy is, I will not hold back. Are you ready?

1010008.name: Goddesses' Moment
1010008.desc: Commander, are you having a good time? Ehehe, I certainly am. It's not often that we get to relax like this. Why don't we head out and enjoy the breeze?

1040001.name: Kizuna AI
1040001.desc: HAI DOMO! Kizuna AI here! Are you the commander I've heard rumors about? It's a pleasure to meet and work with you!

1040001.name: Festive Kizuna AI
1040001.desc: The clothes from the Sakura Empire are so stylish! Commander, since it's a rare occasion, let's go take a look around! Ah, of course, don't forget to run the reel~♪

1040002.name: Elegant Kizuna AI
1040002.desc: Well met. I'm Kizuna AI, the new addition to your base. I will do all in my power to be at least of some use. It is a pleasure meeting you, Commander.

1040003.name: Anniversary Kizuna AI
1040003.desc: Kizuna AI here, wearing a dress, coming at you! Be it concert or combat, I'll give it my all!

1040004.name: Super Gamer Kizuna AI
1040004.desc: HAI DOMO! Virtual Gamer Kizuna AI here! Don't worry, Commander, I've played AL a whole bunch before! ... Wait, I've become a ship now?!

1050001.name: Shirakami Fubuki
1050001.desc: We meet at last! I'm Hololive's virtual fox, Shirakami Fubuki! Commander, now that you've called me, we're gonna have a foxin' good time! Now then, let's get to work!

1050001.name: Beachside Fox
1050001.desc: Tada~! It's your favorite Shirakami Fubuki, Hololive Summer version! Commander, pleased to be your fox!

1050002.name: Tokino Sora
1050002.desc: Hey Commander, it's nice to meet you~! I'm Tokino Sora, a virtual idol affiliated with Hololive! I'll do my absolute best here like I always do! I'll be in your care, so cheer me on, Commander!

1050002.name: Under the Clear Sky
1050002.desc: "Hello, my friends! I hope you're well~! This is Sora, on site at a beach in a slightly different world!" Beach visits just feel so invigorating, don't they? On another note, I can't swim…

1050003.name: Minato Aqua
1050003.desc: G-Good Aquafternoon...! I'm Minato Aqua, the Gamer Maid from Hololive~ U-Ugh... I didn't know I would have to introduce myself in this outfit!

1050003.name: Marine Maid
1050003.desc: Commander, good Aquafternoon~! Nice to meet you, it's Aqua, the Gamer Maid from Hololive! I'll show ya what the strongest maid can do!

1050004.name: Natsuiro Matsuri
1050004.desc: I'm the lovely high school girl affiliated with Hololive, Natsuiro Matsuri!! I love singing and having all kinds of lively conversations with people, so make sure to keep your eyes on me!

1050004.name: Matsuri's Day Off
1050004.desc: I'm the lovely high school girl, now in her extra-pure pajamas, Natsuiro Matsuri! Hey hey, Commander, what do you think? Surprised? Don't gawk at me too much~

1050005.name: Nakiri Ayame
1050005.desc: Be cheery, for here's Nakiri! Ay am Nakiri Ayame, Hololive's virtual demon! Ay have come from the great beyond with my accompanying spirits!

1050005.name: Summertime Nakiri
1050005.desc: Be cheery, for here's Nakiri~! Ay am not used to this outfit and am a little embarrassed... But Ay am Nakiri Ayame, Hololive's virtual demon!

1050006.name: Murasaki Shion
1050006.desc: I am the mastermind magician, Murasaki Shion! Come and be bewitched by my mature, seductive outfit!

1050006.name: Virtual Magician
1050006.desc: Here comes Murasaki Shion, Hololive's famous virtual magician! This world will bear witness to my brilliance!

1050007.name: Ookami Mio
1050007.desc: Good Miovening! I'm Ookami Mio. Over here, I seem to be... some sort of aircraft carrier. Let's get along well.

1050007.name: Summer Vacation
1050007.desc: I changed into my swimsuit, but I wonder if it looks right on me? An outfit like this might make you feel breezier just by looking at it~

1060001.name: Marie Rose
1060001.desc: Hello! Oh... What am I supposed to call you? "Commander"? Got it! My name is Marie Rose. Just call me Marie, okay? I'm counting on your support, Commander!

1060001.name: Devilish Servant Against the Splashing Waves
1060001.desc: Hmm, this swimsuit is pretty cute, but isn't it a bit childish? ...In any case, if you like it, then it's all good!

1060002.name: Honoka
1060002.desc: Um... Are you the Commander? Oh, perfect! It's nice to meet you. My name is Honoka! I don't know how much I'll be able to help, but... let's be friends!

1060002.name: Summer Angel on the Shore
1060002.desc: Whoa, the sea is so pretty~! It's as beautiful as the Venus Islands! I'm so blown away, I don't even feel the heat anymore!

1060003.name: Kasumi
1060003.desc: Are you the Owner of the port? The "Commander"? Hello. My name is Kasumi, I'll be staying here for the foreseeable future. I hope we can both get along on friendly terms.

1060003.name: Springside Mist
1060003.desc: I was amazed to see the port had such a scenic place as this... Truly, you can't go without taking this view in. Right, Commander?

1060004.name: Misaki
1060004.desc: It's nice to meet you! From what I've heard, you're the "Commander," right? I'm Misaki. I have experience with various part-time jobs, so... I'm confident that I can be of help to you all. Let's do our best!

1060004.name: Golden Photoshoot
1060004.desc: A photoshoot? That'd be similar to what I did before coming here, but... um, this swimsuit is a bit much... Commander, is this what you're into? Geez... It's so embarrassing...

1060005.name: Nagisa
1060005.desc: Are you the person who led Misaki to this port? You go by the name... "Commander"? Hmm... I don't know how you sweet-talked her into it, but you're not fooling me. The moment you do anything strange... you better be on guard! My name? It's Nagisa. You... silly dog!

1060005.name: Blue Skies, Good Vibes
1060005.desc: Whew! The wind feels great! ...What are you staring at me like that for, you silly dog? You're the one who said you wanted to go to the beach, remember? To start with, how about... we take a stroll?

1060006.name: Nyotengu
1060006.desc: Oh? You don't seem to fear me... Who might you be? ...I see, so it is you who rules over this place. Then I shall call you "Commander." I am Nyotengu. You would do best to keep me entertained, hehe.

1060006.name: Scarlet-Tinged Hot Spring Vacation
1060006.desc: Oho! To think there was a place with this much class... Not bad! I shall hereby be enjoying my hot springs vacation right here, hehehe.

1060007.name: Monica
1060007.desc: Are you the one in charge here? The "Commander"? I'm Monica, the dealer! Well, dealer-in-training. I know it's sudden, but would you care to gamble with me? The stakes will, of course, be high!

1060007.name: The Ace of Hearts
1060007.desc: "Welcome to Monica's Fantabulous Casino! Where you can have your every whim satisfied!" ...Oh, that doesn't sound very casino-managery? Heheh!

1070001.name: Haruka Amami
1070001.desc: Hello, Commander! I'm the idol, Haruka Amami! I'll do my best to share my dreams with everyone in port! Let's all have a great time together!

1070001.name: A Taste of Tranquility
1070001.desc: Good evening, Commander! Are you also taking a break? If so, let's go get some candied apples and have a little chat~♪

1070002.name: Chihaya Kisaragi
1070002.desc: Pleased to meet you. My name is Chihaya Kisaragi. Are you the one in charge of this port? I look forward to working with you.

1070002.name: Reflections of Heavenly Flowers
1070002.desc: Oh, the fireworks display is starting. I'm planning to meet up with the others after this, but... Why don't we spend some time enjoying the view here first?

1070003.name: Iori Minase
1070003.desc: Hello, hello~! My name is Iori Minase! It's such a pleasure to meet you! ...Huh? There's no need for me to force myself...? Hey, wait a second, what do you mean by that?!

1070003.name: A Little Evening Secret
1070003.desc: Blowing bubbles while sitting on a swing... It might seem a bit childish, but there's nothing wrong with enjoying activities like these every so often.

1070004.name: Azusa Miura
1070004.desc: Why hello, my name's Azusa Miura~ Um, this is a port, right? And these are... shipgirls? Um~ Where exactly am I?

1070004.name: Midsummer Relaxation
1070004.desc: Listening to the wind flow through the chimes on the porch seems to carry the summer heat right away. Commander, would you also like to come unwind with me?

1070005.name: Ritsuko Akizuki
1070005.desc: Pleased to meet you. My name is Ritsuko Akizuki. I was wondering what was going to happen to me when I suddenly got blown away, but... In any case, I'm pleased to make your acquaintance!

1070005.name: Paddle Showdown - Summer Formation
1070005.desc: Sorry, what? A paddle showdown? Commander, please... You play that in a kimono, not a yutaka. But if you insist... If I win, you're buying me an ice cream!

1070006.name: Ami Futami
1070006.desc: Nihihi! I'm the idol, Ami Futami! This place seems awfully lively, just perfect for pranking~! See you around, Commander!

1070006.name: Summer Flowers and Sizzling Beats
1070006.desc: Summer's all about the festivals, and Ami Futami's the queen of festivals! Even the fireworks soaring through the sky can't hold a candle to how brilliant Ami is, so keep your eyes on me, Commander~♪

1070007.name: Mami Futami
1070007.desc: Nihihi~♪ I'm the idol, Mami Futami! You'll get to feast your eyes on how alluring Mami is, so look forward to it, Commander~!

1070007.name: Alluring Festival
1070007.desc: Woah~! They're starting to send up the huge fireworks! ...Hey, Commander, just where are you looking? Did Mami's alluring yukata make you go crazy with desire~?

1080001.name: Rikka Takarada
1080001.desc: Um, my name is Rikka Takarada. I'm still a bit confused about what's going on, but... I guess for the time being, I'm in good hands.

1080001.name: Blue Sky Station
1080001.desc: The train still isn't here yet? ...Oh, what a coincidence to see you here, Commander. Where were you headed?

1080002.name: Akane Shinjo
1080002.desc: Hey there, the name's Akane Shinjo. This rigging looks super cool, like it's right out of a mecha. Now if only there were some kaiju around, that'd be the best...

1080002.name: A Vacation Just for Two
1080002.desc: Welcome back, Commander. You sure brought a lot of goodies back for me, huh? Now then, don't just keep standing there, hurry and come to me~

1080003.name: Hass
1080003.desc: Hello, I'm Hass. I was suddenly blown away to this strange place... But, I guess it seems interesting enough here. By the way, is it okay to shoot some videos here?

1080003.name: Seaside Scoop!
1080003.desc: Hass here. Tonight, we're going to take a walk around the port at night. Aaaand, we even have a special guest– the Commander! ...Psst, hey, look at the camera real quick!

1080004.name: Namiko
1080004.desc: Heyyo, it's Namiko! Uhh, wait, is this that whole getting-reincarnated-in-another-world thing that's been super popular? ...It's not, huh. Well, in any case, nice to meet you!

1080004.name: Miss Street-Wise
1080004.desc: Woo, you're here! So, how was it? This meeting spot was pretty easy to find, right? Welp, let's get going then!

1080005.name: Yume Minami
1080005.desc: Hello, my name is Yume Minami. I've ended up in this world for whatever reason. I'll do my best to contribute to the fleet as a heavy cruiser.

1080005.name: A Dream Upon an Open Windowsill
1080005.desc: How lovely. From here, you can see across the entire port, as well as the shimmering ocean... Oh, Commander, here to enjoy the view with me?

1080006.name: Chise Asukagawa
1080006.desc: Woahhh, I somehow ended up in a totally unknown place... Oh, um, my name's Chise Asukagawa! Since I might be here for a while, thanks for looking after me!

1080006.name: Together, Swimming through the Sky
1080006.desc: Woaah, the sun's coming out! It feels so great outside after the rain... Oh, Commander! Let's take a stroll through the sky together!

1080007.name: Mujina
1080007.desc: Kaiju Eugenicist, Mujina. I suppose I'm a battleship now. Just asking to be sure... There are no kaiju in your world, correct?

1080007.name: Golden Promenade
1080007.desc: You've come as well, Commander? In that case, let's accompany each other back while watching the gingko leaves fall.

1090001.name: Late-Night Alchemist
1090001.desc: Hey there, Commander! Hehe, it's been a long while since I had a sleepover with someone. You know, I've really been looking forward to today. So, what would you like to do first?

1090002.name: Bedtime Memories
1090002.desc: Hehe, today was such a fun day... Oh, good evening, Commander. I was just writing my diary entry for the day. Since you're here, why don't you help me out?

1090003.name: Rest Betwixt Dreams and Reality
1090003.desc: Phew, that's everything taken care of for the day... Huh?! Commander, how long have you been there?! I-I apologize for letting you see my slovenly side... Please, just come over here for now.

1090004.name: Moonlit Encounter
1090004.desc: You shouldn't be up this late. What, you can't sleep? You want to stay up with me? ...Fine, I'll keep you company. I haven't been able to get a wink of sleep anyway.

1090005.name: Fairy Dreamer Beneath the Starry Sky
1090005.desc: An elegant verdure, a pellucid azure. I never knew there was such a lovely place at this port... Oh Commander, are you also out on a nighttime stroll?
